Umubare wiyongereye w'ibimenyetso by'indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19) mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi/umuryango w'ubukungu w'uburayi n'ubw'ubwongereza, kuva ku wa 1 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020
Ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bw'icyorezo cya coronavirus (COVID-19) byerekana imiterere nk'iyo mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, byemeza ko, nubwo biri mu byiciro bitandukanye bitewe n'ibihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje gukwirakwira mu bihugu byose.
Dukurikije ubunararibonye bw'u Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bwihuse bigomba kongera ubushishozi mu guhangana n'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazakenera kwitabwaho mu buryo bwihariye.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, habonetse icyorezo cya Pneumonia kitaramenyekana icyatumye kiboneka mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko intandaro ari coronavirus nshya ubu yitwa coronavirus acute respiratory syndrome 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa na SARS-CoV-2 yitwa indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu byagaragaye ko abagera kuri 80% by'abantu bafite COVID-19 bafite uburwayi bworoheje, urugero nk'ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bufite cyangwa budafite pneumonia, kandi abenshi muri abo barakira.
Mu bantu 14% banduye COVID-19, uburwayi bwa COVID-19 bwiyongera cyane ku buryo bukenera kwitabwaho mu bitaro, naho 6% b'abanduye bakagira uburwayi bukomeye bukenera kwitabwaho byihuse.
Urupfu rw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bitaro ni hafi 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye imiterere y'ibimenyetso by'ubwiyongere bwa COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cyo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'Uburayi (EU/EEA) n'Ubwongereza (Ubwongereza) maze tugereranya ibyo bihugu n'Intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Tugeze aho dutangira kugereranya imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'iy'abari mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yongeye gukwirakwira mu karere kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku isi muri iki gihe gikurikije uko iki gihugu gikurikirana.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu nomero yo ku ya 5 Werurwe ya Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. batangaje ko ari bwo bwa mbere mu Burayi hemejwe icyorezo cya COVID-19 nk'uko byemezwa na OMS.
Mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA, abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe n'u Bufaransa ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarutse mu gihugu bavuye i Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu banduye COVID-19 bari bamaze kugaragara mu bihugu byose 30 bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA n'u Bwongereza (Ubwongereza), aho kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza uyu munsi, abantu 39,768 banduye ndetse n'abapfuye bagera ku 1,727 nibo bamaze kumenyekana, muri bo 17,750 banduye ndetse n'abapfuye bagera ku 1,441 bakaba bari mu Butaliyani gusa.
Kubona umubare w'ubwandu bw'icyorezo cya COVID-19
Mu kigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC), imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu byose byo ku isi, ikururwa n'ibitabo byemewe n'amategeko, urugero nk'ubushikiranganji bw'ubuzima bw'icyo gihugu, abategetsi b'ubuzima mu bihugu n'uturere ndetse na OMS, iherutse gusubirwamo buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima imiterere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, ndetse no kugereranya ayo makuru n'ay'u Butaliyani.
Nk'igihereranyo cy'ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bukomeje, twagize imibare y'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu minsi 14, bityo dufata icyerekezo cy'uburyo COVID-19 yagendaga mu bihugu byose by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA n'Ubwongereza, mu gihe cy'itariki ya 1 Mutarama- 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone kandi, twerekanye umubare munini w'abanduye buri gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani z'igitondo, ugereranyije n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza
Uko ibintu byifashe mu minsi 14 ishize mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza, byagaragaje ko hari ibintu byifashe mu Ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku bihugu byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA n'Ubwongereza muri rusange, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, buza kwiyongera cyane ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020.
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'ubwiyongere bwihuse mu mubare w'abandura babonetse mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byerekanye ko hari ukwiyongera kumeze nk'uko kwa COVID-19 (Ibikoresho by'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'ubwandu bwa COVID-19, mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza ugereranyije n'ubw'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Yashimangiye ko, kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibindi bihugu 15 bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byari byatangaje umubare w'abanduye nk'uw'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu gusa cyangwa bitarenzeho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu byerekana ko umubare w'abatangajwe ko banduye COVID-19 uri kwiyongera cyane mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka Buraya n'Ubwongereza.
Imiterere y'ubwiyongere bwa COVID-19 yafashweho impungenge, igaragaza ko icyorezo cyugarije ibihugu byose ku muvuduko umwe.
Nubwo ibihugu bitandukanye, itandukaniro mu bisubizo by'ubuzima bw'abaturage ku rwego rw'igihugu n'ibisobanuro by'abashobora kuba barwaye COVID-19 bitandukanye mu bihugu ndetse n'amabwiriza atandukanye agenga abagerageza COVID-19, harimo n'ibizamini by'inyongera.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu ntara zangijwe n'icyorezo mu Butaliyani bagaragaje ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi bw'ingufu, kandi amakuru aturuka mu bitangazamakuru avuga ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bw'ingufu mu ntara byamaze kugera ku bushobozi bwuzuye.
Amakuru ku byerekeranye no kwakira abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bitaro no/cyangwa mu byumba by'ubutabazi bwa hafi ubu araboneka ku rwego rwa EU/EEA ku bantu 6% na 1% gusa, buri wese (amakuru ntaragaragazwa).
Ariko kandi, ayo makuru agomba gukusanywa mu buryo bufite gahunda kugira ngo ashyigikire amakuru y'ubugenzuzi iriho yibanda ku mubare w'abamaze kwandura n'umubare w'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bugaragaza itandukaniro rinini mu kuboneka kw'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bwa hafi n'ubwiteganyirize mu Burayi, hagati ya 29.2 mu Budage na 4.2 by'ibitanda ku baturage 100,000 muri Porutugali.
Ibi bivuze ko igihugu gifite umutungo munini ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12.5 ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe n'ubwiteganyirize kuri buri 100,000 abaturage mu 2010).
Imiterere y'ibimenyetso bijyanye n'ubwiyongere bw'ubushobozi bwo kwita ku buzima, hamwe n'ingengo y'imari ku gihugu cya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza ku byerekeranye n'ikwirakwira ry'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bitaro byibasiwe n'ibyago > 90% byo kurenza ubushobozi bw'ibitanda byitabwaho cyane, byatanzwe mu isesengura rya gatandatu ry'igenzura ry'ibyago byihuse kuri COVID-19 na ECDC.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu abarwayi bamaze kuvuka mu turere tw'ibihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bwihariye bikunze kwita ku baturage bo mu turere tw'ibanze, amakuru y'abarwayi n'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bwihariye yagombye kuboneka mu Tatanama y'ibyumba by'akarere by'urwego rw'ibaruramari rwa 2 (NUTS-2).
Ibyaranze Ubutaliyani n'imyitwarire iriho mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje kwiyongera mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bwihuse bigomba rero kwitegura icyiciro cy'icyiciro cy'icyiciro cy'icyiciro cya SARS-CoV-2 n'ubwiyongere bw'abandura COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho mu by'ubuzima, cyane cyane mu buvuzi bwihuse, nk'uko bigenda mu turere twibasiwe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu igenzura ry'ibyago byihuse rya ECDC riherutse, uburyo bwihuse, bwigenga kandi bwimbitse ni ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2, uhereye ku buryo bwo gukumira ukageza ku kugabanya, kuko kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abandura bishobora kudahesha abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro igihe gihagije cyo gusobanukirwa, kwakira no guhindura ibisubizo byabo mu buryo bukwiriye mu gihe bitari byarateganyijwe mbere.
Igenzura ry'ibyago byihuse kandi ryashyizeho ingamba zo kwita ku buzima rusange mu kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari igihe gito cyo kubona uburyo ibihugu bishobora gukomeza kongera ingufu mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya igitutu ku buzima.
Ibi biramutse bitabaye, birashoboka ko sisitemu yo kwita ku buzima mu bindi bihugu bya EU/EEA izahura n'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze kwica abantu barenga 3,000 no kwandura abantu barenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, bituma abantu bahura n'akaga.
Kimwe na virusi ihura na yo, SARS-CoV, yateje SARS mu bantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no gukwirakwira mu byatsi kandi igateza ibimenyetso nk'ibyo binyuze mu buryo nk'ubwo.
Nyamara COVID-19 ifite ubukana buciriritse n'ubwandu buciriritse kurusha SARS ariko ni indwara yandura cyane kandi igera ku bantu bakuru kurusha ingimbi n'abangavu ndetse no ku bagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza umubare wiyongera w'ibitabo bivuga iby'iyo ndwara nshya, iyi ngingo yagerageje gutanga ibisobanuro bihuje n'igihe kandi byuzuye ku birebana n'icyo kibazo cy'ubushakashatsi kigenda kigenda gihinduka.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ibanze byerekeye indwara z'ibyorezo, izifata, izifata, izirwanya n'izirinda.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko iyi nama izadufasha gusobanukirwa no kurwanya iyi ndwara iteza akaga.
Umunsi mukuru wa Spring Festival wo ku wa 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye urwibutso rutunguranye kandi rutazibagirana mu Bashinwa basabwe kuguma mu rugo mu gihe cy'ibiruhuko ndetse no mu byumweru byakurikiyeho kubera icyorezo cy'indwara ya virusi.
Iyo virusi ihuriye cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yatumye habaho indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze (SARS) mu 2003; bityo, yashyizwe ku rutonde rwa SARS-CoV-2 n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ku wa 11 Gashyantare 2020 n'indwara ifitanye isano na yo yitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, gihita gikwira mu gihugu hose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yari imaze guhitana abarwayi barenga 80,000 bemejwe na COVID-19, abasaga 40,000 barekuwe ndetse abasaga 3,000 barapfuye.
OMS yaburiye ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa mbere w'abaturage" kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye cyane kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko tubikesha PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, hamaze gutangwa inyandiko zirenga 2000 ku bijyanye na COVID-19 harimo iby'ubwandu, iby'indwara, iby'imiterere, icyorezo n'uburyo bwo kuyivura, kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku wa 7 Mutarama 2020 yagaragazaga ko virusi yavuye mu barwayi bake.
Iyi ngingo yagerageje gusobanura neza uko ubushakashatsi mu bintu bishya kandi bikomeje kwiyongera bugiye kugenda buhinduka.
Mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, tuzakora ubushakashatsi ku bijyanye na COVID-19 tugereranyije na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na CoV, ari yo Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS, yavutse mu 2012).
Tuzasuzuma n'ibyavuzwe ku birebana n'uko umuntu ashobora kwirinda indwara, uko yayirwara n'ibindi bibazo by'ingenzi.
CoVs zisanzwe zifatwa nk'indwara zidakira abantu, ubusanzwe zikaba ziterwa na 15% by'ibicurane bisanzwe 4.
Nyamara, muri iki kinyejana, twabonye inshuro ebyiri za CoV z'abantu ziteza indwara nyinshi, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye habaho icyorezo cyakomotse mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, nyuma y'aho zahita zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi zifite ubwandu n'urupfu bikabije.
Bityo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu cyanditswe.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa mu Ishusho ya 1,1, icyorezo cya Pneumonia kitaramenyekana inkomoko yacyo cyatangajwe bwa mbere kivuye i Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kigezwa kuri Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima y'u Bushinwa.
Hashize iminsi irindwi, icyorezo cya CoV cyakomeje.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020 nibwo habonetse umuntu wa mbere wapfuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho, iki cyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu mijyi, intara n'ibihugu by'ibituranyi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, habonetse amakuru y'ubwandu mu bakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima, agaragaza ko umuntu ashobora kwandura ku wundi muntu.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan washyizweho itegeko ryo gufunga imiryango, ndetse n'ibikorwa byose by'ingendo rusange byahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bw'ubuvuzi kuri iyo ndwara bwavuze ko, ku barwayi 41 bafite ikibazo cyemejwe, 21 gusa ari bo bari bafitanye umubano n'isoko ry'ibyokurya by'inyanja rya Wuhan ryibonekeza nk'aho ari ho hatangiriye ubwandu buturutse ku bikoko bitazwi.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iyi ndwara ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu ku isi.
Mu gihe cy'iyi raporo, iyi ndwara yari imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo cya 2.2).
Kubera ko ibintu byihuta cyane, ntibiramenyekana niba icyorezo kizarangira cyangwa niba kizakomeza.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bigo byinshi ku barwayi 8,866 harimo 4,021 bemejwe ko barwaye COVID-19 bwatangaga isesengura ry'iki cyorezo nk'iri rikurikira (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
