Nyamara kandi, uburwayi bwo mu mutwe no kubura umwuka ni byo bibangamira cyane abarwayi kandi ni byo bituma abantu bapfa cyane.
Ku bw'ibyo, ubufasha bwo guhumeka ni ingenzi mu guhumuriza ibimenyetso no kurokora ubuzima ndetse burimo imiti rusange ya ogisijeni, ogisijeni y'umurindi mwinshi, guhumeka mu buryo budateye ubwoba no guhumeka mu buryo bwa kimashini, bitewe n'uburemere bw'indwara.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bikaze bagomba gushyigikirwa na oxygenation ya membrane extracorporeal (ECMO), uburyo bwo gukora imashini za cardiopulmonary zinyuranye zikoreshwa mu kuvura umutima cyangwa guhumeka.
Byongeye kandi, kubungabunga ibyangombwa by'amashanyarazi, gukumira no kuvura indwara z'ibanze ndetse n'imihangayiko ya sepsis, no kurinda imikorere y'ingingo z'ingenzi na byo ni ngombwa ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2.
Byamenyekanye ko ibihuha by'imiti bituruka ku kwiyongera kw'imikorere y'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri mu barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Igitutu cya cytokine ni uburyo bwo gusubiza indwara z'ubwonko buzwiho guturuka ku guturika kw'urugaga rw'ibinyabutabire birimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, na MCP-1.
Izi cytokine zituma ingirabuzimafatizo z'umubiri zisohora umubare munini w'ibinyabuzima by'ubwigenge ari na byo bitera indwara ya ARDS n'izindi ndwara ziterwa n'imyanya ndangagingo.
Imiti yo kurwanya indwara ni ingenzi mu kuvura cytocin storms, cyane cyane mu barwayi barwaye cyane.
Kortikosteroide na tocilizumab, anti-IL6 monoclonal antibody, byakoreshejwe mu kuvura cytocin storm.
Ubundi buvuzi bw'imiti yo kurwanya imiti yo mu bwoko bwa cytokine burimo uburyo bwo guhindura uburyo bw'imiti yo mu bwoko bwa T-cells; IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF; JAK; blinatumomab; cytokine 4 signaling suppressor; na HDAC.
Steroids, nk'immunosuppressive, zakoreshejwe cyane mu kuvura SARS mu kugabanya ubukana bw'ingaruka z'ubwandu.
Nyamara, steroid mu miti minini ntabwo ari ingirakamaro ku kwangirika kw'ibihaha bikomeye mu barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19.
Ku rundi ruhande, iyo umuntu afashe steroid nyinshi cyane, bishobora gutuma agira ingaruka zikomeye cyane cyane, cyane cyane indwara yo mu bwonko (osteonecrosis avasculaire), bigatuma ibyago byo gupfa bitamugwa neza.
Icyakora, ingano yo hasi kugeza ku ngero z'ibiro bya koritositeroyide mu gihe gito, byasabwe ko bikoreshwa mu buryo bw'ubwitonzi mu barwayi ba COVID-19 bafite ibibazo bikomeye.
Mu gihe iyi ngingo yandikwaga, nta miti ya virusi ikora neza yari yemejwe.
Icyakora, gukoresha intravenously remdesivir, analogue ya nukleyotide, byagaragaye ko ari byiza ku murwayi w'Umunyamerika wanduye COVID-19.
Remdesivir ni umuti wa antiviral w'icyongereza watangijwe na Gilead mu ntangiriro zo kuvura indwara ziterwa na Ebola na Marlburg.
