Guhinduka no guhinduka byagiye bituma virusi ya corona (CoV) n'izindi ndwara zikomeye, harimo n'abantu, bihoraho mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi.
Mbere ya 2003, abantu babiri bavuye muri CoV (HCoV) bari bazwiho kuba bateza indwara zidakomeye, urugero nk'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cya Sars (Sandrome de la respiration aiguise) na Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS) cyahinduye imyumvire, kigaragaza ukuntu HCoV ari mbi kandi ishobora guhitana ubuzima.
