Indwara ya HCoV ni zoonosis kandi gusobanukirwa inkomoko ya zoonotic ya HCoV bishobora kudufasha.
HCoV nyinshi zituruka mu ducurama zitandura.
Inzego z'ubutabazi z'abandura za HCoV zimwe na zimwe nazo zirazwi.
Kumenya imiterere y'inyamaswa bigira ingaruka ku kwirinda indwara mu bantu.
Ubushakashatsi ku mikoranire y'abaturanyi ba CoV mu nyamaswa bwatumye hagira akamaro ko gusobanukirwa iby'imiterere ya CoV mu bantu.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twatanze isesengura ry'ibyari bimenyerewe ku bantu barindwi barwaye HCoVs, twibanda ku mateka y'ibyavumbuwe, inkomoko ya zoonotic n'uburyo ikwirakwira hagati y'amoko.
Icy'ingenzi ni uko tugereranya no gutandukanya HCoV zitandukanye duhereye ku buryo virusi ihindagurika no kuvugurura genome.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cy'iki gihe cyaganiriweho muri iyi nkuru.
Byongeye kandi, hakomejwe ku kamaro ko guhanahana imiterere y'indwara n'ingaruka zo guhinduka kwa virusi ku ndwara.
Koronavirusi (CoV) ni yo mu muryango wa Coronaviridae, igizwe n'itsinda ry'ubwoko bumwe bwa virusi za RNA z'umugozi umwe, ziterwa n'ubwonko bwiza, ziterwa n'ubwonko.
Ubu burebure bw'iyo genomes buri hagati ya 26 na 32 kilobases kandi ni yo genomes nini cyane mu virusi za RNA kandi yitiriwe "CoV" kubera imiterere yayo isa n'ikamba munsi ya mikrosikopi ya elegitoroniki.
Mu buryo bw'ibanze, virusi za CoV zifite genomes zitagira ibice zigira imiterere imwe.
Biteganyijwe ko bibiri bya gatatu by'iyi genome bifite imiterere y'ibitabo bibiri binini (ORF1a na ORF1b) bihuriyeho, hanyuma bigasobanurwa kuri pp1a na pp1ab polyprotein.
Polyprotein nyuma ikora kugirango ibone poroteyine 16 zitagira imiterere, zizwi nka nsp1~16.
Ibisigazwa by'igitsina bigizwe na ORFs z'ibinyabuzima bifite imiterere, harimo igifu (S), igipfuka (E), uruhu (M) na nukleoproteine (N).
Hariho poroteyine zimwe na zimwe z'inyongera za poroteyine zihariye z'umwirondoro nazo zigena uko umwirondoro wa CoV utandukanye.
Hashingiwe ku itandukaniro ry'urutonde rw'ingirabuzimafatizo, CoVs zashyizwe mu miryango ine (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV), aho ingirabuzimafatizo beta-CoV igizwe na HCoVs nyinshi kandi igabanyijemo imirongo ine (A, B, C na D).
Ibimenyetso bya phylogenetic byerekana ko ibinyugunyugu n'imbeba aribyo bikora nk'isoko ry'imiterere ya alpha-CoV na beta-CoV, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zikora nk'isomero rya gamma-CoV na delta-CoV.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, virusi za CoV zagiye zinyura mu ngorane z'ubwoko, ndetse zimwe muri zo zagiye zigira uruhare mu guhitana abantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana koronavirusi 7 z'umuntu (HCoVs).
