Nk'uko byatangajwe mu kinyamakuru cya karindwi (3 Werurwe 2020), kwemeza ko umuntu yakekwaho indwara bisaba guhuza ikintu kimwe mu bintu by'amateka y'indwara n'ibintu bibiri by'ubwigaraga mu buvuzi kugira ngo hagire igisubizo gifatika, cyangwa se bisaba kuzuza ibintu bitatu by'ubwigaraga mu buvuzi mu gihe nta mateka asobanutse y'indwara:
Amateka y'indwara: (1) Amateka y'urugendo cyangwa kuba mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu duce tuwurimo, cyangwa mu yandi moko aho abarwayi ba COVID-19 bagaragaye mu gihe kitarenze iminsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (2) Amateka y'ubwandu bw'ubwandu bwa SAR-CoV-2 (binyuze mu gupima by'indwara y'ubumara); (3) Amateka y'ubwandu bw'abarwayi bafite umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu nkengero zawo, cyangwa mu yindi midugudu aho COVID-19 yagaragaye mu gihe kitarenze iminsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (4) Amateka y'ubwandu bw'ubwandu bwemejwe bw'icyorezo (((> 2 abarwayi bafite umuriro n'ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero mu gihe kitarenze ibyumweru 2 mu gace gato, nko mu rugo, mu biro, mu ishuri, n'ibindi.
Ibimenyetso by'ubushakashatsi: (1) umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka; (2) bifite ibimenyetso byerekana ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) imibare y'amaraso yera igaragaza imibare isanzwe, igabanuka, cyangwa umubare w'amaraso y'ibinyamushongo ugabanuka mu ntangiriro.
Gushakisha icyemezo cy'uko umuntu yanduye bigomba gushingira ku kuba umuntu akekwaho indwara cyangwa se ku bimenyetso bya serology bikurikira: (1) ibipimo bya PCR by'igihe nyacyo byerekana ko umuntu yanduye SARS-CoV-2; (2) virusi yose mu mikoranire yayo igaragaza ko ifite homogenite yo hejuru ku zindi virusi za coronavirus; (3) IgM na IgG byihariye ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2 mu bipimo bya serum; cyangwa se igorora IgG yihariye kuri SaRS-CoV-2 kuva ku batagira ingano kugeza ku batagira ingano, cyangwa se kongera inshuro > 4 mu cyiciro cyo gukira ku cyiciro cy'icyorezo.
Dushobora kubona ko ibipimo bya PCR by'igihe nyacyo by'indwara ya nucleic acid mu myanya y'ubuhumekero cyangwa mu maraso byongerewe ku byiciro bya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) n'ibya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020).
Gushakisha indwara ziterwa n'amaraso byashyizwe mu gitabo cya kane (ku wa 27 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatanu (ku wa 8 Gashyantare 2020); nyuma y'aho, ibipimo bya serolojiya byashyizwe mu gitabo cya karindwi.
