Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryemeje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo
Ku wa gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryemeje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19  indwara iterwa na coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  ari icyorezo.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryerekeza gusa ku rugero indwara yagezeho, aho kwerekeza ku buryo umuntu ashobora kuyirwara, OMS yamenye ko ari ngombwa gusaba leta kugira icyo ikora:
Ibihugu byose biracyafite ubushobozi bwo guhindura icyerekezo cy'icyorezo.
Niba ibihugu byiboneye, bigerageza, bivura, bica, bikurikirana kandi bigashishikariza abaturage babyo kugira icyo bakora, nk'uko byatangajwe na Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa WHO.
Dufite impungenge zikomeye ku byerekeye ubwandu n'uburemere bw'iki cyorezo ndetse n'ubw'abatabyitabira.
Dukurikije uko Dr. Tom Frieden, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara no Kuzirinda yabivuze, icyorezo "nta ho cyari cyigeze kibaho".
Yavuze ko mu magambo CNN yasohotse muri Gashyantare, "uretse influenza, nta zindi virusi zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero zigeze zigaragara ku isi hose zigikomeje gukwirakwira".
Ghebreyesus na we yavuze ko "nta cyorezo cy'icyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus twigeze tubona".
Yakomeje agira ati "kandi ntabwo twigeze tubona icyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa icyarimwe".
Iyi ndwara yiswe icyorezo nyuma y'icyemezo cyafashwe na OMS muri Mutarama cyo gutangaza ko ari icyorezo cyugarije Isi.
Dr. Anthony Fauci, umuyobozi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Indwara Zandura n'Indwara Zihitana, yavuze ko icyorezo "mu magambo make, kiri kugenda kirushaho kuba kibi".
Kugeza ku wa kane, Associated Press yatangaje ko hari nibura abantu 126,000 banduye COVID-19 ku isi, abasaga 4,600 bakaba barapfuye.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus 201920 ni icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'icyorezo cy'uburwayi bw'ubuhumekero bukabije bwa coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Iki cyorezo cyamenyekanye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Bushinwa, mu Ukuboza 2019, cyatangajwe nk'Icyorezo cy'Ubuzima Mpuzamahanga ku ya 30 Mutarama 2020, cyatangazwa nk'icyorezo ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, bikaba byarabahitanye bagera ku 97,000.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 barakize.
Imibare y'abapfa yagaragajwe ko ari 4% mu Bushinwa, mu gihe ku isi hose bari hagati ya 13.04% muri Alijeriya na .08% muri Nouvelle-Zélande.
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe ni umuriro, gucumba no guhumeka nabi.
Ibibazo bishobora kuvuka harimo uburwayi bw'ibihaha n'indwara y'umuvuduko mwinshi wo guhumeka.
Igihe cyo guhishurirwa ibimenyetso ubusanzwe kiba iminsi itanu, ariko gishobora kuba hagati y'iminsi ibiri n'icumi n'ine.
Nta rukingo cyangwa umuti wihariye wa virusi bizwi.
Ubuvuzi bw'ibanze ni ubuvuzi bw'ibimenyetso n'ubufasha. Ingamba z'ubwirinzi zasabwe harimo gukaraba intoki, gupfuka umunwa mu gihe cyo gukorora, kwirinda abandi, no kugenzura no kwigunga ku bantu bakeka ko banduye.
Abategetsi hirya no hino ku isi bitabiriye ibyo bikorwa bashyiraho amategeko yo kwirinda ingendo, gushyira abantu mu kato, gushyiraho amategeko yo kwirinda abantu, kugenzura akaga mu kazi no gufunga ibigo.
Iki cyorezo cyateje imvururu ku isi yose mu by'ubukungu n'imibereho, guhagarika cyangwa guhagarika ibikorwa by'imikino, iby'idini, ibya politiki n'iby'umuco, ndetse n'ubukene bw'ibikoresho by'ubwikorezi bwatewe n'ubucuruzi bw'agahinda.
Amashuri na za kaminuza byafunzwe mu bihugu byose cyangwa mu turere twose mu bihugu 193, bigira ingaruka ku banyeshuri bagera kuri 99.4% by'abari mu mashuri.
Amakuru atari yo kuri virusi yageze kuri interineti, kandi hari n'ibimenyetso by'urwikekwe n'ivangura ku Bashinwa, abandi bantu bakomoka mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo y'Amajyepfo ya Aziya n'abo mu turere dufite ubwandu bukomeye.
Kubera ko ingendo zagabanyijwe n'inganda zikomeye zifunze, habayeho kugabanuka kw'umwuka wanduye ndetse n'umwanda wa karuboni.
Abayobozi b'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Bushinwa (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei) batangaje ko hari hamaze kugaragara icyorezo cya pneumonia itaramenyekana ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, kandi iperereza ryatangiye mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Abenshi muri abo bantu bakomeretse bafatiwe mu isoko rya Huanan ryagurishwaga ibiribwa by'inyanja, bituma bakekwaho ko virusi ifite inkomoko mu nyamaswa.
Virusi yateje icyorezo cyiswe SARS-CoV-2, virusi iherutse kuvumburwa ifitanye isano ya hafi na coronavirus y'ikinyugunyugu, coronavirus y'inguge, na SARS-CoV. Umuntu wa mbere uzwiho kugaragaza ibimenyetso by'iyi ndwara yaje kugaragara ko yarwaye ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, kandi uwo muntu nta sano yagiraga n'ibizamini by'isoko ry'amazi byakurikiyeho.
Mu itsinda rya mbere ry'abarwayi ryavuzwe mu Ukuboza 2019, bibiri bya gatatu by'abo barwayi bagaragaye ko bafitanye isano n'isoko.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, raporo itari yemewe y'ikinyamakuru South China Morning Post, yagaragaje ko umuntu umwe wongeye kugaragara ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo 2019, mu murwayi w'imyaka 55 wo mu ntara ya Hubei, ashobora kuba ari we wa mbere. Ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko, mu gihe habonetse abarwayi bashya baturuka mu Bushinwa ariko bakubita mu gitutu mu Butaliyani, Irani na Korea y'Epfo, umubare w'abarwayi bashya hanze y'Ubushinwa warenze uw'abarwayi bashya bo mu Bushinwa ku ncuro ya mbere.
Hashobora kuba hari umubare uhwanye w'abatavuzwe, cyane cyane mu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Kugeza ku ya 26 Gashyantare, umubare muto w'abanduye wari umaze kugaragara mu rubyiruko, aho abafite imyaka 19 n'abari munsi yayo bangana na 2.4% by'abanduye ku isi. Umujyanama mukuru w'ubushakashatsi mu Bwongereza, Patrick Vallance, avuga ko 60% by'Abongereza bagomba kwandura mbere y'uko haboneka ubwirinzi bw'urugaga.
Abarwayi ni umubare w'abantu bapimwe COVID-19, kandi bapimwe bagasanga barwaye nk'uko amategeko abiteganya.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyakoze ibizamini birenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi ibihugu byinshi byamaze gushyiraho politiki yo kudakora ibizamini ku bantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje gusa, nk'u Butaliyani, u Buholandi, Esipanye n'u Busuwisi.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku ya 16 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku ya 23 Mutarama, abagera kuri 86% by'abanduye COVID-19 bataraboneka, kandi ko abo barwayi bataraboneka ari bo batumye haboneka 79% by'abanduye.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ibaruramari bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 30 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abandura mu Butaliyani urenze uw'abari babimenyeshejwe.
Igereranyo cy'ibanze cy'umubare w'ubwiyongere (R0) kuri COVID-19 ni 1.4 kugeza kuri 2.4.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, bwagaragaje ko uwo mubare ushobora kuba ari 5.7.
Abantu benshi bafite COVID-19 barakira.
Ku batagaragazaga ibimenyetso, igihe cy'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara kugeza bapfuye cyari hagati y'iminsi 6 na 41, ariko akenshi cyabaga iminsi 14.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97,000 bapfuye bishwe na COVID-19.
Mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku wa 5 Gashyantare, hafi 80% by'abapfuye bari mu bafite imyaka 60 n'iyirenga, naho 75% bafite ibibazo by'ubuzima harimo indwara z'umutima na diyabete.
Umubare w'abapfa by'ukuri bazira COVID-19 ushobora kuba ari munini cyane, kuko ushobora kuba utari ukubiyemo abapfa batageragejwe - urugero nko mu ngo, mu bigo byita ku barwayi, n'ibindi.
Imibare y'igice cy'ubwandu bw'u Butaliyani igaragaza ko umubare w'abapfuye muri iki cyorezo warenze umubare w'abapfuye bishwe na COVID ku buryo bwa 4-5x.
Umuvugizi w'umugore w'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) yavuze ko "tuzi ko [umubare w'abapfuye wavuzwe] ari umubare muke", amagambo ashyigikirwa n'amakuru y'ibyavuzwe ku mubare muto w'abapfuye muri Amerika.
Urupfu rwa mbere rutari mu Bushinwa rwabaye ku ya 1 Gashyantare muri Filipine, naho urwa mbere rutari muri Aziya rwabaye ku ya 14 Gashyantare mu Bufaransa.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, hanze y'Ubushinwa, abantu barenga 12 bapfuye muri buri gihugu, muri Irani, Koreya y'Epfo no mu Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu n'uturere birenga mirongo ine byatangaje ko hapfuye abantu, ku mugabane wose uretse Antarctica.
Iyi mibare itandukanye bitewe n'akarere ndetse n'igihe, kandi igira ingaruka ku mubare w'ibizamini, ireme ry'uburyo bwo kwita ku buzima, uburyo bwo kuvura, igihe kuva icyorezo cyatangira, n'ibintu by'abaturage birimo imyaka, igitsina, n'ubuzima muri rusange.
Dukurikije imibare ya Johns Hopkins University, igipimo cy'abapfuye ku isi hose ni 6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020.
Ibyo bitekerezo biva mu karere kamwe bikagera mu kandi.
Mu Bushinwa, ingano y'abapfa bishwe n'uburwayi yavuye kuri 17.3% (ku bantu bafite ibimenyetso byatangiriye ku itariki ya 1/10 Mutarama 2020) igera kuri 0.7% (ku bantu bafite ibimenyetso byatangiriye ku itariki ya 1 Gashyantare 2020). Ibindi bipimo birimo igipimo cy'abapfa bishwe n'uburwayi (CFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abapfuye bazize indwara, n'igiciro cy'abapfuye bazize indwara (IFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abazize indwara (bazize indwara ndetse n'abazize indwara) bapfa bazize indwara.
Izi mibare ntizihuza n'igihe kandi zikurikirana abaturage runaka uhereye ku ndwara ukageza ku byemezo by'ubwandu.
Hari intiti nyinshi zagerageje kubara umubare w'abantu bafite ubwo burwayi.
Ikigo cy'Ubushakashatsi ku Bihereranye n'Ubuvuzi cya Kaminuza ya Oxford gitangaza ko umubare w'abahitanywe n'icyorezo cy'icyorezo muri rusange uri hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
