Ariko muri iki gihe, nta kintu gifatika gishobora kuvugwa cyerekana igihe ibyo bizabera".
Umujyanama mukuru w'ubuvuzi muri leta y'Ubushinwa Zhong Nanshan yavuze ko "icyorezo gishobora kurangira muri Kamena" mu gihe ibihugu byose byabasha gukurikiza inama za WHO ku ngamba zo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu ishuri ry'i Londres ryigisha iby'isuku n'imiti y'ubushyuhe bw'ikirere yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 "izakomeza gukwirakwira, wenda mu gihe cy'umwaka umwe cyangwa ibiri".
Nk'uko bigaragazwa n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na kaminuza ya Imperial College, buyobowe na Neil Ferguson, imyitozo ngororamubiri n'ibindi bikorwa bizakenerwa "kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rumaze kuboneka (usanga ruzamara amezi 18 cyangwa arenga)".
William Schaffner wo muri kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yagize ati "Ntekereza ko bishoboka ko iyi coronavirus idashobora guhita ihita ikurwaho burundu kuko ishobora kwandura cyane, kandi ko ishobora kuba ari indwara y'ibihe by'umwaka, igaruka buri mwaka".
Ingaruka mbi z'uko izongera kugaragara zizaterwa n'uko ubwoko bw'umuntu bufite ubwirinzi n'uko yahindutse.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe kandi umuntu wafashwe na byo ashobora kuba adafite ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara cyane ni umuriro (88%) n'igisebo (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara harimo umunaniro, guterwa umwotsi wo guhumeka (umwotsi), kubura impumuro, guhumeka nabi, kubabara imitsi n'imitsi, kuribwa mu muhogo, umutwe, ubukonje, kuruka, hemotipisi, diarrhea cyangwa cyanotic.
Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika cyandika ibimenyetso by'ubudahangarwa nk'ububabare bwo guhumeka, ububabare cyangwa igitutu gihoraho mu gatuza, kwibeshya bitunguranye, kugorwa no kubyuka, no kugira amaso cyangwa iminwa y'ubururu; kwitabwaho byihuse iyo ibi bimenyetso bibayeho.
Bamwe mu bantu banduye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso, nta bimenyetso by'ubuvuzi bafite ariko bagasanga hari ibipimo byemeza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi bagatanga inama ko abantu bagiranye isano ya bugufi n'abantu banduye bagomba gukurikiranwa hafi no gusuzumwa kugira ngo barebe ko nta ndwara bafite.
Ubushinwa buvuga ko umubare w'abatazi ibimenyetso uhera kuri 44% ugera kuri 7%.
Igihe cy'ubuhumekero (igihe hagati y'ubwandu n'intangiriro y'ibimenyetso) gitangirana n'umunsi umwe kugeza ku minsi 14; ubusanzwe ni iminsi itanu. Nk'urugero rw'ibidasobanutse, ugereranyije umubare w'abantu bafite COVID-19 batakaza ubushobozi bwo kumva akamoto mu ntangiriro ni 30% hanyuma ugabanuka ugera kuri 15%.
Ibindi bisobanuro ku buryo iyi ndwara ikwirakwira biracyateganyijwe.
Byitezwe ko iyi ndwara yandura cyane cyane mu gihe cyo gushyikirana cyane no mu gihe cyo gukorora, kwitsamura cyangwa kuvuga; aho gushyikirana cyane biba biri hagati ya metero 1 na 2 (metero 3 na metero 6).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gucumba udakingiye byatuma udutonyanga tw'amazi tuva ku metero 4.5 (15 ft) kugera ku metero 8.2 (27 ft).
Bamwe batanze igitekerezo cy'uko virusi ishobora no kwandura binyuze mu matembabuzi mato aguma mu kirere igihe kirekire, ashobora guturuka mu mvugo.
Ayo mata ashobora kugera mu kanwa cyangwa mu mazuru y'umuntu uri hafi aho cyangwa se ashobora gushyirwa mu bihaha.
Bimwe mu bikorwa by'ubuvuzi nk'intubation na cardiopulmonary resuscitation (CPR) bishobora gutuma ubwonko bw'umuntu buva mu myanya y'ubuhumekero buva mu mwuka, bityo bigatuma umwuka utera.
Iyi virusi ishobora gukwirakwira iyo umuntu akoze ku bice byanduye, harimo n'uruhu, hanyuma agakora ku maso, ku zuru cyangwa ku kanwa.
Nubwo hari impungenge ko virusi ishobora gukwirakwira mu byondo, iki kibazo cy'ubwandu giteganyijwe kuba gito.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yahakanye ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura mu kanwa binyuze mu byo umuntu anywa. Iyo virusi yandura mu minsi itatu ya mbere nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso, ariko ishobora kwandura mbere y'uko ibimenyetso biboneka no mu gihe cy'indwara.
Abantu bapimwe neza ku ndwara kugeza ku minsi itatu mbere yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso byerekana ko kwanduzanya bishobora kuba byarabaye mbere y'uko ibimenyetso biboneka.
Hari raporo nke z'abandura batagira ibimenyetso zemejwe na laboratoire, ariko ubwandu bw'abandura batagira ibimenyetso bwagaragajwe n'ibihugu byinshi mu iperereza ry'ibanze.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) kivuga ko nubwo bitamenyekana neza uburyo indwara yandura, umuntu umwe ubusanzwe yandura abandi babiri cyangwa batatu. Virusi iguma ku butaka amasaha menshi kugeza ku minsi.
By'umwihariko, basanze virusi ishobora kugaragara mu gihe cy'iminsi itatu ku plastiki (polypropylene) n'icyuma kitagira ingese 304, ku munsi ku makarito, no mu gihe cy'amasaha ane ku muringa.
Ibi ariko biratandukanye bitewe n'ubushyuhe n'ubushyuhe.
Nta bimenyetso bigaragaza ko inyamaswa zishobora kwanduza abantu, ariko abategetsi b'u Bwongereza batanga inama yo gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukora ku nyamaswa, nko nyuma yo gukora ku bindi bice bishobora kuba byarakoreweho n'abantu banduye.
Indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze cyane ya coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ni virusi nshya, yabanje gutandukanywa n'abantu batatu barwaye pneumonia ifitanye isano n'icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze i Wuhan.
Ibintu byose biranga virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 bibaho mu buryo bufatika ku mikorobe mu bidukikije. Uretse umubiri w'umuntu, virusi yicwa n'isabune zo mu nzu, zisenya udupfukamunwa twazo. SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano ya hafi na SARS-CoV y'umwimerere.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba ifite inkomoko mu nyamaswa.
Ubushakashatsi ku bimera bwagaragaje ko koronavirusi ziterwa n'ibinyabuzima byo mu bwoko bwa Betacoronavirus, mu bwoko bwa Sarbecovirus (ubwoko bwa B) hamwe n'ibindi bimera bibiri byaturutse mu bwoko bw'ibinyabuzima byitwa bat.
Iyo virusi ifite 96% y'ubwoko bwa virusi ya coronavirus y'ikinyugunyugu (BatCov RaTG13) ku rwego rw'ibanze rw'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima.
Muri Gashyantare 2020, abashakashatsi bo mu Bushinwa babonye ko hari itandukaniro rimwe gusa rya aside muri porogaramu imwe ya genomic ya virusi y'inguge n'iy'umuntu.
Itandukaniro rya jenome yose kugeza ubu ryagaragaje ko 92% by'ibinyabuzima by'umuntu ari byo byashyizwe hamwe hagati ya coronavirus ya tenglewine na SARS-CoV-2, ibyo bikaba bitari bihagije kugira ngo hagaragazwe ko tenglewine ari yo yateye.
Kwandura virusi bishobora gutangwa mu gihe gito hakurikijwe ibimenyetso, nubwo amaherezo byemezwa hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo kwandika imiterere y'urufunguzo rwa polymerase-reaction (rRT-PCR) ku byimba byanduye cyangwa se hakoreshejwe ibizamini bya CT.
Ubushakashatsi bwagereranyije PCR na CT i Wuhan bwagaragaje ko CT ari ingenzi cyane kurusha PCR, nubwo atari yo yihariye, kuko ibyinshi mu bimenyetso byayo byerekana ko ifata imyanya y'ubuhumekero n'izindi ndwara.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, Ishuri ry'Abanyamerika ry'Imiyoborere ryasabye ko "CT itakagombye gukoreshwa mu gupima cyangwa nk'igenzura rya mbere ryo gupima COVID-19".
OMS yashyize ahagaragara amabwiriza y'igerageza rya RNA kuri SARS-CoV-1, ya mbere ikaba yasohotse ku ya 17 Mutarama.
Ikizamini gikoresha uburyo bwo guhindura inyandiko mu gihe cy'ukuri (rRT-PCR).
Ibi bishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero cyangwa amaraso.
Ibisubizo by'ibizamini ubusanzwe biboneka mu masaha cyangwa mu minsi mike.
Ubusanzwe ibi bizamini bikorwa hakoreshejwe isapu yo mu mazuru ariko isapu yo mu muhogo nayo ishobora gukoreshwa.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, nta na kimwe muri ibi bipimo cyagaragaye ko ari cyiza ku buryo cyakwemerwa gukoreshwa ku buryo bwagutse.
Muri Amerika, ibipimo bya serology byakozwe na Cellex byemewe gukoreshwa mu bihe by'ubutabazi n'ibigo byemewe gusa.
Ibimenyetso by'ibimenyetso by'imashini mu byuma bya radiographie na tomographie (CT) by'ibinyamushongo birimo ubwiyongere bw'ibirahuri by'ubutaka by'ibisigisigi bitameze kimwe n'igihombo cy'ibirahuri kitariho.
Ishyirahamwe ry'abakora ibizamini by'imikorere y'ubumara mu Butaliyani ririmo rikusanya amakuru yo kuri interineti agamije gushakisha amashusho y'abamaze kwandura.
Kubera guhangana n'izindi ndwara nka adenovirus, imikorere y'imikorere ya PCR ifite umwihariko ku kumenya COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bunini mu Bushinwa bwagereranyije ibipimo bya CT y'igituza na PCR kandi bugaragaza ko nubwo amashusho atari ayo kwihariye ku ndwara, uburyo bwa vuba kandi ari bwo bworoshye, bigasaba ko ubwo buryo bwakoreshwa nk'igikoresho cyo gupima mu turere tw'icyorezo.
Imikorere y'imikorere y'ubwonko ishingiye ku bwenge bw'ubumenyingiro bw'ibanze yateguwe kugira ngo ishobore kumenya virusi yifashishije amashusho ya radiographie na CT.
Uburyo bwo kwirinda kwandura indwara harimo gukomeza kugira isuku, gukaraba intoki, kwirinda gukora ku maso, amazuru cyangwa umunwa utarakaraba, no gukorora cyangwa gukorora ku bikoresho hanyuma ukabishyira mu myanda.
Abafite ubwandu basabwe kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu ruhame.
Ingamba zo kwirinda kwanduza umubiri nazo zasabwe kugira ngo birinde ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo.
Nyamara, iyi virusi imaze kugera ku rwego rwo kwanduza abaturage mu bice byinshi by'isi.
Ibi bivuze ko virusi ikwirakwira mu baturage, kandi bamwe mu baturage ntibazi aho cyangwa uburyo bayanduye. Abashinzwe ubuzima bita ku muntu ushobora kwandura barasabwa gukoresha ingamba zisanzwe zo kwirinda, ingamba zo kwirinda guhura, no kurinda amaso.
Gukoresha amakuru y'aho umuntu ari kuri telefoni ngendanwa ku bw'izo mpamvu byateje impungenge z'ibanga, aho Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe asaga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko hakorwa ingamba zo kugabanya ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura.
Porogaramu zitandukanye za mobile zashyizweho cyangwa zashyizweho ku bushake, kandi kugeza tariki ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda arenga icumi arimo gukora ku bisubizo byububiko, nko gukoresha Bluetooth kugirango umenye aho umuntu ari hafi ya telefoni.
Abakoresha nyuma bahabwa ubutumwa niba bari bafitanye umubano n'umuntu wagize ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19.
Nta rukingo rwa COVID-19, nubwo imiryango myinshi irimo gukora kugira ngo ikore urukingo.
Gukaraba intoki ni ingenzi mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo.
CDC isaba ko abaturage bakaraba intoki kenshi bakoresheje isabune n'amazi nibura amasegonda makumyabiri, cyane cyane nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero cyangwa igihe intoki zisa n'izanduye; mbere yo kurya; na nyuma yo guhumeka, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Ibyo biterwa n'uko iyo virusi iri hanze y'umubiri w'umuntu, yicwa n'isabune yo mu nzu, igatwika icyo gikingira.
CDC ikomeza isaba gukoresha umuti wo gusukura intoki ukoreshwa inzoga ufite nibura 60% by'inzoga iyo nta sabuni n'amazi bihari.
OMS irasaba abaturage kwirinda gukora ku maso, amazuru cyangwa umunwa intoki zitabanje gukaraba.
Ubuso bushobora kwanduzwa nibintu byinshi (mu gihe cyumunota umwe wo koherezwa ku muti wica imyanda kubutaka bwicyuma kitagira ingese), harimo 62% ya etanol, 50% ya isopropanol, 0.1% ya sodium hypochlorite, 0.5% ya peroxide ya hidrogeni, na 0.27.5% ya povidon-iodin.
Ubundi buryo bwo kuboneza urubyaro, urugero nka benzalkonium chloride na crohexidine gluconate, ntibukora neza.
CDC iratangaza ko mu gihe hari umuntu ukekwaho cyangwa wemejwe ko arwaye COVID mu bigo nk'ibiro cyangwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi, ahantu hose hakoreshwa ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki, nk'ibikoresho byo mu rwego rwa elegitoroniki, ibyuma by'ikoranabuhanga, ibyuma by'ibanga, ibyuma by'ibikoresho bya kure n'imashini za ATM zikoreshwa n'abantu barwaye, bigomba gukingirwa.
Imiryango y'ubuzima isaba abantu ko bakinga umunwa n'amazuru yabo n'amaboko cyangwa umwenda igihe bakorora cyangwa basese, kandi ko bakwirinda uwo mwandiko.
Amasasu y'ubuvuzi ni ingirakamaro ku bantu bashobora kwandura, kuko kwambara masike bishobora kugabanya umubare n'uburebure bw'amazi atemba mu gihe umuntu avuga, atinya, kandi akorora.
OMS yashyizeho amabwiriza ku gihe n'uburyo bwo gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Stephen Griffin, umuhanga mu by'indwara z'ubwandu muri Kaminuza ya Leeds, yagize ati "Kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya abantu kugendana n'amaso yabo, ari yo soko y'icyorezo iyo badafite isuku yo mu ntoki".
OMS yashyizeho amabwiriza y'uko abantu bafite amagara mazima bambara agapfukamunwa mu gihe bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, urugero nk'abita ku bantu bafite COVID-19, nubwo yemeza ko kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda gukorakora mu maso.
Ibihugu bimwe byatangiye gushishikariza abantu gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Muri Amerika, CDC isaba abantu kwambara udupfukamunwa tutari utwo kwa muganga twakozwe mu myenda. Ubushinwa bwasabye abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza gukoresha udupfukamunwa twa muganga tw'ibanze, cyane cyane iyo bahuye n'abandi bantu bari hafi (metero 1 (n'ibirenge 3) cyangwa munsi yayo).
Hong Kong irasaba kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe ukoresha imodoka cyangwa mu gihe uri ahantu hakunzwe abantu benshi.
Abashinzwe ubuzima muri Thailand bashishikariza abaturage gukora udupfukamunwa tw'umwenda mu ngo zabo no kuzajya tuzikaraba buri munsi.
Repubulika ya Tchèque na Slovakiya bibuza abantu kujya mu ruhame batambaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa batwikiriye umunwa n'amazuru.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye abantu bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu ruhame kugira ngo bibarinde n'abandi.
Guverinoma ya Otirishiya yashyizeho itegeko ry'uko abantu bose binjira mu maduka bagomba kwambara agapfukamunwa.
Israel yasabye abaturage bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu ruhame.
Tayiwani, imaze gukora udupfukamunwa miliyoni 10 ku munsi kuva mu kwezi kwa gatatu, yasabye abagenzi bo mu mihanda ya gari ya moshi n'amabisi gutwara abantu mu mujyi kwambara udupfukamunwa ku itariki ya 1 Mata.
Panama yasabye abantu kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari hanze, ndetse inasaba abantu kudatunga udupfukamunwa mu ngo zabo.
Ibipfamatwi nabyo byatangiye gukoreshwa cyane mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Malaysia na Singapore.
Gutegereza abantu (byitwa no gutotezwa) bijyanirana n'ingamba zo kurwanya ubwandu zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara binyuze mu kugabanya umubano wa bugufi hagati y'abantu.
Uburyo harimo ubwigenge; guhagarika ingendo; no gufunga amashuri, aho ukorera, sitade, inzu mberabyombi cyangwa amazu y'ubucuruzi.
Abantu bashobora gushyira mu bikorwa ingamba zo kwirinda mu buryo bw'imibereho binyuze mu kuguma mu ngo zabo, kugabanya ingendo, kwirinda ahantu hari abantu benshi, gukoresha imashini zitagira abantu, no kwitandukanya n'abandi.
Ubu leta nyinshi zisaba cyangwa zisaba abantu kwirinda mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Ingano y'iteraniro ry'abantu benshi cyane ryasabwaga n'inzego za leta z'Amerika n'imiryango y'ubuzima, ryagabanyijwe mu buryo bwihuse riva ku bantu 250 (niba nta cyorezo cya COVID-19 kizwi muri ako karere) rijya ku bantu 50, hanyuma rijya ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwabujije amateraniro rusange y'abantu barenga babiri. Abantu bakuru n'abafite ibibazo by'ubuzima by'ibanga nka diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko ukabije w'amaraso, n'ubwirinzi bufite intege nke bahura n'ibyago byo kurwara indwara zikomeye n'ibibazo kandi bagirwa inama na CDC kuguma mu rugo bishoboka mu turere dufite icyorezo cy'umuryango.
Gukoresha ijambo "uburoko bw'imibanire" byagiye bituma abantu bagombye kwiherera mu buryo bwuzuye, aho kubashishikariza kuvugana n'abandi mu bundi buryo.
Muri byo harimo inama yo kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'umuntu utuye hamwe gusa, udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso byayo.
Kwigumira mu ngo byasabwe ku bantu basanganywe COVID-19 ndetse n'abakekwaho kuba barayanduye.
Inzego z'ubuzima zatanze amabwiriza arambuye yo kwicungira ukwabo mu buryo bukwiriye. Leta nyinshi zategetse cyangwa zasabye ko abaturage bose baba mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo bibohoka.
Amabwiriza yo kwicungira ukwabo akomeye cyane yashyizweho ku bantu bari mu byiciro by'abashobora kurwara.
Ababa baragaragaye ku muntu ufite COVID-19 n'ababa barigeze kujya mu bihugu cyangwa uturere dufite ubwandu bw'icyorezo basabwe kwicungira ukwabo mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe bashobora kuba baraherukaga kugaragara.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura icyorezo ni ukucyumira cyangwa kucyicisha, no kugihosha.
Gukumira byakozwe mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo kandi bigamije gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abanduye no gushyiraho ubundi buryo bwo kugenzura ubwandu no gukingira kugira ngo indwara ihagarare mu baturage basigaye.
Iyo bitagishoboka ko indwara yandura, ibikorwa by'ubutabazi bihinduka ku cyiciro cyo kugabanya: ingamba zifatwa zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo no kugabanya ingaruka zayo ku rwego rw'ubuzima ndetse n'abaturage.
Guhuza ingamba zo gukumira no kugabanya bishobora gukorwa icyarimwe.
Ingamba zirasabwa ingamba zikomeye zo guhagarika icyorezo binyuze mu kugabanya umubare w'ababyara hasi ya 1. Kimwe mu byo pda ikora mu gucunga ikwirakwira ry'indwara zandura ni ugushaka kugabanya icyorezo, bizwi nka kugabanya icyorezo.
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo kuremerera serivisi z'ubuzima no gutanga igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'ubuvuzi.
Ingamba zidakoreshwa mu buvuzi zishobora gucunga ikwirakwira zirimo ingamba zo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nko kugira isuku y'amaboko, kwambara udupfukamunwa, no kwishyira mu kato; ingamba z'abaturage zigamije gutandukanya abantu nk'amashuri gufunga no guhagarika amateraniro manini; guhuza abaturage mu rwego rwo gushishikariza kwakira no kwitabira izo ngamba; kimwe n'ingamba z'ibidukikije nko gusukura ubutaka. Ingamba zikomeye kurushaho zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira zafashwe mu Bushinwa nyuma y'uko icyorezo cyigaragaje, urugero nko gushyiraho ihagarikwa ry'umujyi wose no gukomera ku itegeko ryo kwirinda ingendo.
Ibindi bihugu na byo byafashe ingamba zitandukanye zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho uburyo bwinshi bwo kugenzura no gushyira abantu mu kato, ndetse itanga n'impanuro ku bijyanye n'aho umuntu wafashwe na virusi itera SIDA ashobora kujya.
Singapuru itanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku bantu banduye bakomeza kwigenga kandi igahana bikomeye abatishoboye.
Taiwan yongereye umusaruro w'ibikoresho byo mu maso kandi isaba ibihano byo gukwirakwiza imiti. Imiterere yo mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika yerekana ko kugabanya (kugabanya ariko kutahagarika ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) no kugabanya (guhagarika icyorezo cyateye imbere) bifite imbogamizi zikomeye.
Politiki yo kugabanya cyane ishobora kugabanya ibyangombwa by'ubuzima ku kigero cya 2/3 n'urupfu ku kigero cya 50%, ariko bigakomeza gutuma abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana bapfa, kandi bigatuma imibereho y'abarwayi irushaho kuzamba.
Ingamba zishobora kuba ari amahitamo ariko zigomba gukomeza igihe cyose virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rumaze kuboneka, niba ari rwo rwabanje), kuko ikwirakwira ryayo rizongera guhita ryiyongera mu gihe ingamba zo kwirinda zizaba zarorohewe.
Gufata ingamba z'igihe kirekire zo guhashya icyorezo byateje ingaruka ku bukungu no ku mibereho y'abaturage.
Nta muti wa virusi wemewe ku buryo bwihariye wa COVID-19, ariko ibikorwa byo kuwukora birakomeje, harimo no kugerageza imiti ihari.
Kurya imiti ya grippe, kunywa amazi no kuruhuka bishobora kugufasha kugabanya ibimenyetso byawe.
Bitewe n'uburemere bw'iyo ndwara, bishobora gukenerwa ko umuntu afata umwuka wa ogisijeni, agafata amazi mu maraso ndetse n'ubufasha bwo guhumeka.
Gukoresha imiti ya siporo bishobora gutuma ingaruka z'ibyo bikorwa zirushaho kuba mbi.
Bimwe mu bintu byari byemewe kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi birimo gushakishwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS ivuga kandi ko hari "uburyo bwo kuvura mu buryo busanzwe no mu rugo" bushobora gufasha mu kugabanya ibimenyetso by'indwara ya SARS-CoV-19.
Kongera ubushobozi no guhuza ubuzima bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bivugwa na OMS nk'ingamba z'ibanze zo guhangana n'icyorezo.
ECDC n'ibiro by'umuryango w'abibumbye byita ku buzima mu karere k'Uburayi byatanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'imirimo y'ubuzima mu rwego rwo gukusanya umutungo mu byiciro bitandukanye, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu gukora ibizamini bya COVID-19, guhagarika uburyo bwo kwihitiramo igihe bibaye ngombwa, gutandukanya no gushyira mu kato abarwayi ba COVID-19 bafite ubwandu, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 binyuze mu guhugura abakozi no kongera umubare w'abahumeka umwuka n'ibitanda.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku bijyanye n'aho ikibazo cya mbere (cyitwa icy'umubare ubusa) cyavuye.
Icyorezo cya mbere cya coronavirus cyamenyekanye ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan, Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wariyongereye buhoro buhoro.
Iyi ndwara ahanini ifitanye isano n'isoko rya Huanan Seafood Wholesale Market, na ryo rigurisha inyamaswa nzima, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi ikomoka mu bwoko bumwe bw'inyamaswa; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, ifite inkomoko ya zoonotic.
Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan babwiye bagenzi babo ko bari bafite "virusi ya SARS".
Abo baganga umunani, barimo Li Wenliang, bari barahawe umuburo n'abapolisi kubera gukwirakwiza ibihuha, naho undi, Ai Fen, yari yarakosowe n'abayobozi be kubera ko yari yahagurukije ibyo bintu.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umurenge wa Wuhan nyuma yasohoye itangazo ku mugaragaro ku wa 31 Ukuboza imenyesha OMS.
Abaturage bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan batanze raporo y'uko hari abantu benshi barwaye indwara ya kanseri y'ibihaha, mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa mbere.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati muri Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu bindi bice by'Ubushinwa, ifashwa n'ubwimukira bw'umwaka mushya w'Ubushinwa, maze Wuhan iba ihuriro ry'ingendo ndetse n'ahantu hakomeye ho gutembereza gari ya moshi.
