COVID-19 yemejwe ko yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020 iturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko habonetse ubwandu bwinshi bw'abarwayi bemejwe ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare, ahanini bikaba byatewe n'amateraniro yabereye i Daegu y'ishyaka rishya ry'idini ryitwa Shincheonji Jesus Church.
Abashyigikiye Shincheonji bari baje i Daegu baturutse i Wuhan bakekwaho kuba ari bo batumye iki cyorezo cyandura.
Kugeza ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9,336 b'iryo dini, abantu 1,261 cyangwa abagera kuri 13% bavuze ko bafite ibimenyetso.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 2,000 bemejwe ko banduye muri Koreya, ku ya 29 Gashyantare bari 3,150.
Inzego zose za gisirikare za Koreya y'Epfo zahawe akato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu basuzumwe basanga bafite virusi.
Amatariki y'indege na yo yaragoretswe, bituma ayo marushanwa ahinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda ivugwaho kuba ari yo yagutse kandi iteganyijwe cyane ku isi yo kugenzura abaturage kugira ngo bamenye virusi, no gutandukanya abantu bose banduye no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu bahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura burimo kwiyamamaza ku mugaragaro ku bimenyetso by'abashya baturutse mu mahanga binyuze kuri porogaramu za terefone ngendanwa, gupima virusi byakozwe ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu bagera ku 20,000 bapimwa ku munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo yafashwe nk'iyigenga mu kugenzura icyorezo nubwo nta mujyi wose wahawe ubwigenge.
Abenshi mu baturage ba Koreya basinye ku nyandiko basaba ko Moon yirukanwa ku mpamvu bavuga ko ari uko leta yarenze ku mabwiriza yari yatanze yo kurwanya icyorezo, cyangwa se ko yashimye uko yabyitwayemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo yari ifite umubare muto w'abanduye buri munsi mu byumweru bine.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata abantu bose bageraga mu mahanga bazajya bakorerwa icyumweru cya kabiri cy'igihembwe.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'itangazamakuru ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ubutumire bw'ibihugu 121 byo gufasha mu gupima virusi.
Irani yatangaje ku nshuro ya mbere icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 cyemejwe ku ya 19 Gashyantare i Qom, aho nkuko Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi bw'Ubuvuzi ibivuga, abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma y'uwo munsi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zatangajwe na leta harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'indi mihango y'umuco, imikino, n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, no gufunga kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yashyizeho miliyari eshanu z'amafaranga yo kurwanya virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twibasiwe n'icyorezo, ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi yatangaje muri Werurwe, nubwo urujya n'uruza rwari rwinshi hagati y'imijyi mbere ya Nowruz y'umwaka mushya w'Abaperesi rwakomeje.
Gucumbikira Abasilamu mu mujyi wa Qom byatangiye ku mugaragaro kugeza ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Nubwo havuzwe ko icyorezo cya Iran cyagaragaye, ibihugu birenga icumi byakurikiranye abakize muri Irani kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, bigaragaza ko icyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha 388 leta ya Irani yari imaze gutangaza kugeza kuri uwo munsi.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, aho 23 mu badepite 290 bayigize bagaragaye ko banduye virusi ku ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abagororwa bo muri Irani kurekura byanze bikunze abarwanashyaka bazira imyigaragambyo y'amahoro, no kurekura imfungwa zose zifite uburenganzira bwo gufungwa by'agateganyo.
Yavuze ko hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwiza virusi mu bigo by'imfungwa, aho usanga nta buvuzi buhagije.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko hapfuye abantu 100 ku munsi, umubare munini wa mbere w'abantu bapfuye muri icyo gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 n'abakozi ba leta cyangwa abahoze ari bo bamaze guhitanwa n'iyo ndwara.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari ifite abarwayi bashya 50 buri saha n'urupfu rushya buri minota 10 kubera coronavirus.
Abategetsi ba OMS bavuga ko mu gihugu cya Irani hari abantu bakubye inshuro eshanu abo byatangajwe.
Yongeyeho ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'igihugu mu by'imari bwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Komisiyo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye y'Uburenganzira bwa Muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu byoroherezwa ibihugu byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Iki cyorezo cyemejwe ko cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubwo ba mukerarugendo babiri b'Abashinwa bapimwe ko banduye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Abanduye batangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose zijya n'izava mu Bushinwa ndetse itangaza ko ari mu bihe by'ubukungu.
Amatsinda y'abantu badafite ubwandu bwa COVID-19 yaje kugaragara nyuma, atangira n'abantu 16 bemejwe muri Lombardy ku ya 21 Gashyantare. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inteko y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya ryo kugenzura icyorezo, harimo no gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50,000 baturutse mu turere 11 dutandukanye two mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani.
Minisitiri w'intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "Mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo, kwinjira no gusohoka ntibizemerwa.
Gufunga imirimo n'imikino byategetswe muri ako karere".Ku ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na kaminuza bifungwa burundu mu gihugu hose ubwo u Butaliyani bwageraga ku mubare w'abapfuye 100.
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo n'imikino ya Serie A, yagombaga kuba mu nzu kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yahagaritswe burundu mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse guhagarika ibikorwa byose by'ubucuruzi usibye amasoko manini n'amafashini. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ishuri ry'Ubuvuzi, Ubuvuzi, Gusubiza no Gukiza (SIAARTI) ryasohoye inama z'imico y'ubuvuzi ku bijyanye na protokoli ya triage ishobora gukoreshwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwatsinze Ubushinwa mu bihugu bifite umubare munini w'abapfa ba coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutanga raporo y'abantu 3,405 bishwe n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje indege icyenda z'ingabo zitwaye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hemejwe ko abantu 128,948 banduye, 15,887 barapfuye, naho 21,815 bakira, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu ntara ya Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN ivuga ko guhuza umubare munini w'abantu bakuze mu Butaliyani no kutabona uburyo bwo gupima abantu bose banduye virusi kugeza ubu bishobora kuba ari byo bituma habaho urupfu rwinshi.
Igisubizo cy'Ubwongereza kuri virusi cyabanje kugaragara nk'igihugu cyifashe neza kurusha ibindi, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'Ubwongereza ntiyigeze ishyiraho uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kwirinda abantu cyangwa ingamba zo gushyira abantu mu kato.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko leta yaje kunengwa kubera ko yabonetse idafite umuvuduko n'ubunyangamugayo mu gusubiza impungenge abaturage bahanganye nazo. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje inama yo kwirinda ingendo zose zidakenewe no gutumanaho, asaba abaturage gukora kuva mu rugo igihe bishoboka no kwirinda ahantu nko mu tubari, mu masoko, no mu bibuga by'imikino.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, leta yatangaje ko ahantu ho gusangira hose nko muri pub no muri gym hagomba gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi isezeranya ko izishyura abakozi bagera kuri 80% by'umushahara kugeza ku gipimo cya £2,500 ku kwezi kugirango birinde ubushomeri muri icyo cyorezo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'intebe yatangaje ingamba zo gukumira abantu, kubuza guteranira hamwe abantu barenga babiri no kugabanya ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze kubyo byemejwe ko ari ngombwa.
Bitandukanye n'ingamba zabanje, iyi myigaragambyo yashyizweho n'abapolisi binyuze mu gutanga amasoko no guhagarika amateraniro.
Ubucuruzi bwinshi bwahawe amabwiriza yo gufunga, uretse ubucuruzi bufatwa nk'"ingenzi", harimo amasoko, ibicuruzwa, amabanki, amaduka acuruza ibikoresho by'ibikoresho, sitasiyo ya lisansi, n'amazu y'ubwubatsi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko arwaye COVID-19 yemejwe mu ntara ya Pacific Northwest ya Washington mu mugabo wari uherutse kuva i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Itsinda ry'abashinzwe kurwanya Coronavirus ryashyizweho ku ya 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu rusange, ndetse bushyiraho n'amabwiriza yo guhagarika ingendo z'abashyitsi baturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura indwara - ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cya leta ya Amerika - cyatangaje ko cyateguye uburyo bwacyo bwite bwo gupima.
Nubwo bimeze bityo, Amerika yatangiye gutinda mu gupima, ibyo bikaba byirinda icyorezo cy'icyorezo muri iki gihe.
Ibizamini byagize ingaruka mbi kubera kit yo gupima yangiritse yatangijwe na leta muri Gashyantare, kubura kwemerwa na leta ku byuma by'ipimisho bitari ibya leta (ibikoresho bya kaminuza, ibigo n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, n'ibipimo bihamye ku bantu bakwiriye gupimwa kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (bitangazwa na muganga nyuma yaho).
Kugeza ku ya 27 Gashyantare, The Washington Post yatangaje ko hateganyijwe ibipimo by'ibanze by'abantu munsi ya 4,000 muri Amerika.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko hateganyijwe ibipimo bike cyane birenga 14,000.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko "abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso n'amabwiriza y'abaganga bari bamaze amasaha cyangwa iminsi bategereje gupimwa". Nyuma y'urupfu rwa mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika rwamenyekanye muri leta ya Washington ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko ari mu bihe by'ubutabazi, ibintu byaje gukurikiraho vuba na bwangu n'izindi leta.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, kandi mu kwezi kwa gatatu amashuri yo mu gihugu hose yari afunze. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatanze ingengabihe y'ingaruka za coronavirus nshya ku gihugu cyayo n'itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo muri Imperial College London.
Kuri uwo munsi Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ryo gutanga inkunga y'inyongera yo kwitegura no gusubiza coronavirus, riha miliyari $8.3 mu nkunga y'ubutabazi ku bigo bya leta mu rwego rwo gusubiza iki cyorezo.
Isosiyete yashyizeho ingamba zo gukumira ingendo z'abakozi, guhagarika inama, no gushishikariza abakozi gukora bavuye mu rugo.
Imikino n'ibirori by'imikino byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko yahagaritse ingendo mu bice byinshi by'u Burayi, uretse Ubwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Bukeye bwaho, yaguye uwo muteguro awugeza mu Bwongereza no muri Irilande.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko igihugu gifite ikibazo cy'ubukungu, bituma amafaranga ya leta aboneka kugira ngo iki kibazo gikemuke.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ubucuruzi bwinshi bwafunze cyangwa bugabanya amasaha yo gukora muri Amerika yose mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyemejwe mu bihugu byose 50 no mu Ntara ya Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko umujyi wa New York City ufite 10,700 by'abanduye coronavirus, kurusha umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko kwirinda abantu kugaragara nk'ibisanzwe, kuko imibare y'abanduye yatangiye kugabanuka kuva ku minsi 2.0 ikagera ku minsi 4.7.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, hari abantu 32,308 bemejwe ko banduye muri New York City, naho 672 bahitanywe na virusi. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zavuze ko zifite abantu benshi banduye coronavirus kurusha ibindi bihugu byose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'itangazamakuru ku wa 30 Werurwe, Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Trump, yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu ku buryo budafite aho bubogamira kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bwitwaga USNS Comfort, bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1.000, bwashyize amarembo mu mujyi wa New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zari zimaze guhitana abantu 884 mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Muri leta ya New York, abanduye barengaga 100.000 ku itariki ya 3 Mata. White House yanenzwe kubera ko yagabanyije iterabwoba no kugenzura ubutumwa mu gutegeka abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi guhuza itangazamakuru n'ibyavugiwe kuri virusi n'ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Kwemera muri rusange ubuyobozi bwa Trump kuri icyo kibazo byatangiye ku mpande zose z'ishyaka.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Amerika n'abarezi banenze Amerika bitewe no kugura ibintu by'ingenzi, harimo n'imiti, ivuye mu Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'ingendo zo mu kirere ryakoreshejwe mu gupima no guhanura uburyo bwo kwanduza ndetse ryasohotse mu kinyamakuru The Journal of Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa Mutarama 2020.
Hashingiwe ku makuru yo mu mwaka wa 2018 yatanzwe n'ishyirahamwe mpuzamahanga ry'ingendo z'indege, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo, na Taipei ni byo bihugu bya mbere byabonye umubare munini w'abashyitsi baturutse i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byatangajwe ko ari byo bihugu bikunzwe cyane n'abava i Wuhan.
Bali yagaragaye nk'umurwa w'ibigo 20 by'ingenzi by'uturere bidakoreshwa cyane mu bijyanye n'ubwikorezi, mu gihe umujyi wo muri Ositaraliya wagaragaye ko ari wo ufite ubushobozi bwinshi. Australia yashyizeho gahunda yo guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) ku ya 7 Gashyantare.
Yavuze ko hari byinshi bitaramenyekana kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga mu kugenzura imipaka no gutumanaho mu gusubiza icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, mu gihugu cya Ositaraliya hashyizweho itegeko ry'umutekano w'ibinyabuzima.
Mu gihe hashyizweho ingamba zo gushyira mu kato ingendo rusange muri Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateguye kwimura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba diplomasi mu karere, byiganjemo ingendo z'indege zahawe igihugu cy'amavuko, nyuma y'uko abategetsi b'Ubushinwa babimwemereye.
Kanada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, u Buhindi, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, u Bufaransa, Argentine, u Budage na Tayilande, ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere byari byateguye kwimura abaturage babyo.
Pakisitani yavuze ko itazongera kohereza abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Brazil yacyashye Abanya-Brasil 34 cyangwa imiryango yabo usibye Abanyapolonye bane, Umunyashinwa umwe, n'Umuhindi umwe.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, mu Bushinwa no mu Buhinde, bahawe ubutaka muri Polonye, aho indege y'Abanyamerika yahagaritse mbere yo gukomeza urugendo rwayo igana muri Brezili.
Aba-Barazil bari bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasilia.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abanyakanada 215 (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere, na 39 bari mu ndege ya kabiri yari yaraguzwe na leta ya Amerika) bavuye i Wuhan bajyanwa ku biro by'indege bya CFB Trenton kugira ngo bahamare ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abakanada 185 ivuye i Wuhan yageze ku kibuga cy'indege cya CFB Trenton.
Abategetsi ba Australia bimuriye abaturage 277 ku itariki ya 3 n'iya 4 Gashyantare mu kigo cy'imfungwa cya Christmas Island, cyahindutse ahantu ho kwigumira, aho bamaze iminsi 14.
Indege y'ubutabazi ya New Zealand yageze muri Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (harimo bamwe baturutse muri Australia no muri Pasifika) bari bamaze igihe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangaje ko zizakura Abanyamerika mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye Abanyakanada 129 bari bavuye muri Diamond Princess yageze i Trento, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa gatatu, leta y'Ubuhinde yatangiye guhungisha abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yari ihawe serivisi na leta ya Afurika y'Epfo yohereje abaturage 112 bo muri Afurika y'Epfo.
Iperereza ry'ubuzima ryakorewe mbere yo kurekurwa, kandi abaturage bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus barasiwe kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abaturage ba Afurika y'Epfo bageragejwe nabi ni bo bonyine boherejwe mu gihugu cyabo.
Ibyavuye mu igeragezwa byemeje ko abaturage bose ba Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abakozi bo mu ndege, abapilote, abakozi bo muri hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, nk'ingamba zo kwirinda, bose bashyizwe mu kato kandi bakamara iminsi 14 mu kigo cya The Ranch Resort.
Muri Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukuraho igice cy'ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'u Bushinwa yavuze ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje imfashanyo mu Bushinwa.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bifatanyije mu gufasha kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'Ubushinwa byibasiwe na virusi, hamwe n'itsinda ry'abantu bo mu karere ka Chicago, byatangajwe ko bagejeje udupfukamunwa 50,000 tw'ubwoko bwa N95 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko batanze miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ya OMS kugira ngo bashyigikire ubushakashatsi ku rukingo n'ubuvuzi, hamwe no kurinda "abaturage bafite ibyago muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo".
Interaktions yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Philippines ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapore yatangaje ko igiye kohereza imfashanyo ingana na $2.26 miliyoni z'amadolari y'Amerika mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze agapfukamunwa ka miliyoni imwe muri Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereza toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje impano ya miliyoni 18 z'intoki z'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwohereza ibikoresho bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi birimo imyenda 10,000 ya Hazmat, na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa no gusezeranya izindi miliyoni 100 z'amadolari mu buryo bw'inkunga y'amafaranga ku bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo. Nyuma y'uko abarwayi mu Bushinwa batangiye kugabanuka, iki gihugu cyatumye imfashanyo mu bihugu byinshi byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje imfashanyo y'ubuvuzi n'impuguke mu gufasha u Butaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje imfashanyo z'ibikoresho byagenewe gupima abantu miriyoni 1.1, udupfukamunwa miriyoni 6 n'imyambaro 60,000 yo kurinda ubuzima i Addis Ababa muri Ethiopia, kugira ngo bitangirwe n'Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yo kohereza ibikoresho 5,000 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'ibikoresho bitanu byo guhumeka, byoherejwe muri Panama.
Ma kandi yatanze imfashanyo z'imiti muri Canada. Ubuholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Georgia, na Repubulika ya Czech batangaje impungenge zabo ku biganiro by'amasasu n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Esipanye yakuye ibikoresho 58 000 byo gupima coronavirus byakozwe n'Abashinwa ku kigero cya 30% gusa, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwasubije mu gihugu cyabo udupfukamunwa 600 000 tw'Abashinwa twari twarangiritse.
U Bubiligi bwasubiye mu bihugu by'amavuko 100,000 by'udupfukamunwa tutakibasha gukoreshwa, twitwa ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, imfashanyo z'u Bushinwa zakiriwe neza mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije igikorwa cy'ubutabazi bw'ibanze ku bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye cyane ingamba leta y'Ubushinwa yafashe zo kugenzura no kugenzura icyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu mwaka wa 2002-2004, ubwo leta y'Ubushinwa yajyaga ishinjwa kugira ibanga ku buryo byabangamira ibikorwa byo kwirinda no kugenzura, n'icyorezo cyo muri iki gihe, aho leta y'u Bushinwa "yagiye itanga amakuru buri gihe kugira ngo abantu batagira ubwoba mbere y'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza ku cyemezo cya guverinoma y'ikigo cyo gushyiraho ingendo muri Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko nubwo "bitagomba kuba ari inama yatanzwe na OMS", ari "ikimenyetso cy'ingenzi cyane ku byifuzo byo kugenzura icyorezo aho cyibasiwe cyane" agita "ikitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange".Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ikwirakwira ry'abantu ku bantu hanze y'Ubushinwa no kwiyongera kw'imibare mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi rusange ku rwego mpuzamahanga (PHEIC), PHEIC ikaba ari iya gatandatu icyo cyorezo cya mbere kigabwe kuva icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cyabaye mu 2009.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa WHO Tedros Adhanom yavuze ko PHEIC ari ingaruka z " "ibyago byo kwandura ku isi cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amafaranga make n'agati mu gihugu bidafite sisitemu nziza y'ubuzima.
Mu gusubiza ku itegurwa ry'imihango yo kwirinda ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zituma ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi bibangamirwa mu buryo budakwiriye" kandi ko "WHO idashishikariza abantu kugabanya ubucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye isi yose gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira gahunda z'iterambere mu bihugu bikennye, ivuga ko ari ngombwa gushyigikira ibihugu "bitafite uburyo bwo kumenya abantu banduye virusi, mu gihe yaba yongeye kugaragara".
Tedros yakomeje atanga itangazo avuga ko "turi abanyembaraga ku mugozi wacu woroshye" asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "kushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura nyuma".Ku wa 11 Gashyantare, mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru, OMS yashyizeho COVID-19 nk'izina ry'indwara.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni Antonio Guterres yemeye guha "ububasha umuryango wose wa Loni mu buryo bwo kwitabira".
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bibazo by'ikibazo ryashyizweho, rituma habaho guhuza ibisubizo byose by'umuryango w'abibumbye, WHO ivuga ko bizatuma "bishyira imbere ibikorwa by'ubuzima mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora kuzana ubuhanga mu guhangana n'ingaruka zikomeye z'iki cyorezo ku mibereho, ubukungu n'iterambere".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'abakozi ba China ba Joint Mission ryayobowe na WHO ryashyizweho kugira ngo ritange ubuhanga mpuzamahanga na WHO mu gihugu cya China mu gufasha mu gucunga mu gihugu no gusuzuma "ubukana n'ubwandu bw'iyo ndwara" binyuze mu gukora amahugurwa n'inama n'inzego z'igihugu zikomeye no gukora ingendo zo gusubiramo kugira ngo harebwe "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza mu turere n'imidugudu, harimo n'imidugudu n'imidugudu".Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, WHO yatangaje ko "isi igomba gukora byinshi kurushaho mu kwitegura icyorezo cya coronavirus" ivuga ko nubwo hakiri kare cyane ko cyitwa icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba "gukora imyiteguro".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo cyagendaga kigaragara muri Irani, OMS yoherejeyo itsinda ry'abakozi ba Joint Mission ngo barebe uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, umukozi wa OMS yavuze ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ku isi kizazamurwa kiva ku "cyinshi" kigashyirwa ku "cyinshi", ari na cyo kigero cyo hejuru cy'ibyavuzwe n'ibyavuzwe.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda z'ubutabazi bw'ubuzima bwa WHO, yatanze umuburo mu itangazo rye agira ati "iyi ni raporo y'ukuri kuri buri butegetsi ku isi: Haguruka.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira kandi ugomba kwitegura", asaba ko ingamba zo kwitabira neza zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibihe bibi cyane".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu atemerera abakozi b'ubuzima rusange gutangaza ko hari icyorezo cyugarije isi, avuga ko "mu by'ukuri twemera ko abantu bose ku isi bashobora kwandura".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko WHO "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ubwiyongere bw'icyorezo n'uburemere bwacyo, n'ubwiyongere bw'ubushomeri bwacyo". WHO yahuye n'ibitekerezo bikomeye ku byo yabonye nk'ubuyobozi butari bwiza bw'icyorezo, harimo gutinda gutangaza ko ari icyorezo cy'ubuzima rusange no gushyiraho icyorezo.
Ibyifuzo birimo n'ibisabwa kugira ngo umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, asezere, byasinywe n'abantu 733.000 kugeza ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu za ONU zibarirwa mu macumi zashimangiye uburenganzira bwa buri muntu ku giti cye mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo guhabwa ubufasha burokora ubuzima kandi ko leta ifite inshingano yo kubikora.
Iryo tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura umutungo cyangwa ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima atari impamvu yo gutandukanya abantu.
Impuguke zagaragaje ko abantu bose bafite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abagize amoko mato, abageze mu za bukuru, abatishoboye, abatagira aho baba, abafite ibibazo bikomeye, imfungwa, impunzi n'andi matsinda akeneye ubufasha bwa leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ishinzwe imiyoborere irimo gukemura ingaruka z'icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku bukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Ibihugu by'i Burayi ryashyizeho urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru ajyanye n'igihe kandi yuzuye ku bijyanye n'ibitekerezo by'amabwiriza mu bihugu byo ku isi, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku ngamba zo gukomeza sisitemu y'ubuzima n'ubukungu bw'isi kugeza ku kuganira ku ngaruka z'ibiza n'ibihano byo gutembera, ibigo bya digitale birimo Iperereza ku Mategeko Nshinga y'Igihugu, bigamije gufasha ibihugu kwigira ku bindi no koroshya igisubizo cy'isi yose cy'ihangana na coronavirus.
Leta y'u Bushinwa yanenzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Minisitiri w'Ubwongereza ushinzwe ibiro bya Guverinoma Michael Gove n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brazil Jair Bolsonaro witwa Eduardo Bolsonaro nyuma yo kugenzura icyorezo, cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abakozi b'intara bo mu ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa (CPC) birukanywe kubera uburyo bwo gukora mu kato mu Bushinwa rwagati, mu rwego rwo kugaragaza kutishimira uko inzego za politiki zabyitwayemo mu guhangana n'icyorezo mu ntara.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bemeza ko iyi myigaragambyo igamije kurinda Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti ry'u Bushinwa Xi Jinping uburakari bw'abaturage ku cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Abategetsi b'Abashinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian, bahakanye itangazo rya mbere ry'uko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyaturutse i Wuhan, bemeranya n'ibitekerezo by'abahuza umugambi w'uko COVID-19 yaturutse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
