Gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu gihe cy'amasaha runaka y'umunsi, bifasha kwirinda indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'igituntu n'igituntu, byandurira mu kanwa binyuze mu byondo.
Umuntu ashobora kandi kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero nka grippe cyangwa se ibicurane bisanzwe, urugero, iyo adakarabye intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, ku zuru cyangwa ku kanwa (urugero, mu mucosa).
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu gihe cy'amanywa bigaragaza ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ingenzi harimo: mbere na nyuma yo gukaraba, nyuma yo gusukura umwana cyangwa guhindura umwenda, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya na mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukorana n'inyama mbi, amafi cyangwa inyoni.
Niba nta mazi n'isabune bihari, ushobora gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umukungugu.
Mbere, mu gihe no nyuma yo gutegura amafunguro.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku barwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindura amadarubindi cyangwa gukaraba abana bamaze gukoresha ubwiherero.
Nyuma yo guhumeka, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ku byokurya byayo cyangwa ku byondo byayo.
Isuku y'amaboko mu by'ubuvuzi yerekeza ku bikorwa by'isuku bifitanye isano n'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gufata imiti cyangwa gukora ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Intego nyamukuru yo gukaraba intoki ni ukuzikuramo indwara ziterwa n'udukoko (bakteriya, virusi cyangwa izindi mikorobe zishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho by'ubumara bishobora guteza akaga cyangwa indwara.
Ni ingenzi cyane cyane ku bantu bakoresha ibiribwa cyangwa bakora mu by'ubuvuzi, ariko ni na ngombwa ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, coronavirus n'izindi ndwara zandura; gukumira inkomoko y'indwara z'ibicurane; kugabanya ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero;
no kugabanya umubare w'abana bapfa bavukiye mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwo mu 2013 bwagaragaje ko imyitwarire myiza yo gukaraba intoki izatuma habaho ukwiyongera guke mu burebure bw'abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero n'indwara z'igituntu ushobora kugabanuka binyuriye mu gushyiraho ibintu byoroheje byo mu myitwarire, urugero nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Iyo ntambwe yoroshye ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abahitanwa n'iyo ndwara ku kigero cya 50%.
Gahunda yo gukaraba intoki ishobora kugabanya ibice by'ibicurane ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, kandi ibyo bishobora kugereranywa no gutanga amazi meza mu duce dufite amikoro make.
Kugabanya ibice 48% by'ibicurane bishobora guterwa no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bwonyine bw'ingirakamaro kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda ibicurane n'ubwandu bw'ubuhumekero (ARI), nk'uko imyitwarire isanzwe ikorwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage hirya no hino ku isi.
Pneumonia, ari yo ARI y'ibanze, ni yo ihitana abana benshi cyane bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, igahitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Indwara y'igituntu na pneumonia hamwe bihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 3.5 buri mwaka.
Dukurikije ibyavuzwe na UNICEF, gushyiraho akamenyero ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya na nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero bishobora gukiza abantu benshi kurusha inkingo imwe cyangwa imiti yose, bikagabanya urupfu rw'indwara y'ibicurane hafi icya kabiri, n'urupfu rw'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye hafi kimwe cya kane.
Gukaraba intoki ubusanzwe bijyanirana n'ubundi buryo bwo kwirinda umwanda nk'igice cy'umugambi w'amazi, isuku n'isuku (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki bishobora no kurinda impetigo yandura binyuze mu gushyikirana ku buryo butaziguye.
Ingaruka mbi yo gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane ni uko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutuma urukoba rwangirika bitewe no gukama kw'uruhu.
Ubushakashatsi bwo muri Danimarike bwo mu 2012 bwerekanye ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ibibyimba, indwara y'uruhu rw'intoki izwi ku izina rya eczema cyangwa dermatitis y'intoki, ikaba ikunze kugaragara mu bakozi b'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane na byo byagiye bigaragara ko ari kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara yo guhangayika bikabije (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu bikomeye ku munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ingenzi mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cy'umwanda mu kanwa: nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero (kugeza, gukaraba), nyuma yo gusukura umwana (kuvanaho umwenda), mbere yo kumusuhuza, mbere yo kurya na mbere/nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukorana n'inyama mbi, amafi cyangwa inyoni.
Indi minsi yo gukaraba intoki neza kugirango wirinde kwandura indwara ni mbere na nyuma yo kuvura igisebe cyangwa igisebe; nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa guhumeka; nyuma yo gukora ku byondo by'amatungo cyangwa gukora ku matungo; no nyuma yo gufata imyanda.
Imibare y'abantu bakaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune iri hasi mu bihugu byinshi.
Mu mwaka wa 2015, ubushakashatsi ku gukaraba intoki mu bihugu 54 bwerekanye ko ku kigereranyo, 38.7% by'ingo zifite akamenyero ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Mu mwaka wa 2014, ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ifite 97 ku ijana; Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ziri hagati na 77 ku ijana; n'Ubushinwa ku kigero cyo hasi cya 23 ku ijana.
Porogaramu y'Ubuzima bw'Ingenzi ishyirwa mu bikorwa na Minisiteri y'Uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa by'inganda mu rwego rwo guteza imbere ubuzima n'uburezi bw'abana.
Gukorora kabiri mu mwaka, hamwe no gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabune, no gusukura amenyo buri munsi n'amavuta, ni byo byibanze muri iyi gahunda y'igihugu.
