Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi bya COVID-19
Gucunga ibyago mu kazi kuri COVID-19 ni uburyo bwo gukoresha uburyo bwo kurwanya ibyago mu kazi mu gukumira icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kugenzura neza akaga mu kazi biterwa n'aho ukorera n'inshingano ufite, hashingiwe ku igenzura ry'ibyago by'aho wabonetse, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage, n'impamvu z'ibyago ku mukozi wese ushobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ikigo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA), akazi gafite ibyago bike byo kwandura kagomba kugira aho gaherera ku kazi gafite aho gaherera ku kazi gafite aho gaherera ku kazi gafite aho gaherera ku kazi gafite aho gaherera ku kazi gafite aho gaherera ku kazi gafite aho gaherera ku kazi gafite aho gaherera ku kazi, aho ingamba zo kwirinda kwandura zisabwa harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu bitaro mu gihe bari mu bitaro, kwirinda guhumeka, no kubahiriza isuku isanzwe n'isuku mu kazi.
Akazi gafite ibyago byo kwandura byoroheje gakubiyemo akazi gasaba guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegerana n'umuntu utazwi cyangwa ukekwaho kuba afite COVID-19, ariko ushobora kwandura bitewe n'icyorezo cy'icyorezo kiri mu baturage cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Ibyo birimo abakozi bafite aho bahurira n'abaturage nk'amashuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo hakennye cyane, n'ahandi ho guhaha hakunzwe cyane.
Mu rwego rwo kugenzura ibyago by'aba bantu, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, harimo guhumeka hakoreshejwe ibikoresho bihumanya umwuka bikora cyane, kwirinda kwitsamura no kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi mu gihe umuntu ahanganye n'umuntu ufite COVID-19.
OSHA ifata abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubuzima n'abakora mu nzu y'ibanga bagaragarijwe abantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bafite COVID-19 nk'abafite ibyago byo kwandura, bikongera ibyago byo kwandura cyane iyo abakozi bakoze uburyo bwo gukora aerosol kuri, cyangwa gukusanya cyangwa gutunganya ibipimo by'abantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bafite COVID-19.
Kugenzura ibyago bikwiye kuri aba bakozi birimo kugenzura ubwubatsi nk'ibyumba by'ubushyuhe bufite imbaraga nke n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bikwiye ku kazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba batitabira akazi kubera uburwayi, kwita ku bandi cyangwa gutinya ko bashobora kuboneka.
Uburyo bwo gucuruza bushobora guhinduka, haba mu bijyanye n'ibicuruzwa bisabwa, n'uburyo bwo kubona ibicuruzwa (nk'ukugura inyuma y'amasaha y'ikiruhuko cyangwa binyuze mu serivisi zo kohereza cyangwa gutwara abantu).
Amaherezo, gutumiza ibicuruzwa mu turere twihariye twibasirwa na COVID-19 bishobora guhungabana.
Gahunda ikemura ibyago bijyanye n'imyanya itandukanye y'akazi n'imirimo y'akazi harimo isoko y'ibyago, ibyago bituruka mu rugo no mu baturage, n'ibyago by'umukozi ku giti cye nk'imyaka y'iza bukuru cyangwa uburwayi budashira.
Nanone kandi, isobanura ingamba zikenewe kugira ngo abantu bakemure ibyo byago, n'uburyo bwo kwirinda icyorezo.
Gutegura no gusubiza indwara zandura bishobora gushingira ku byemezo by'igihugu cyangwa by'igihugu.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'ibibazo bikomeye by'ubuzima, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi, no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi bigo mu nzego z'ibikoresho byabo.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage aho ubucuruzi bubarizwa bugira ingaruka ku bisubizo byafashwe.
Urutonde rw'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa ni uburyo bukoreshwa cyane mu buzima n'umutekano mu kazi kugira ngo ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa.
Iyo COVID-19 idashobora gukurwaho, uburyo bwo kugenzura neza cyane ni ubuhanga, hakurikiraho ubuyobozi, hanyuma hakurikiraho ibikoresho byo kwirinda.
Gucunga imikorere birimo gukumira abakozi mu bintu bishobora kubateza akaga mu kazi, bitagendeye ku myitwarire y'abakozi, kandi bishobora kuba igisubizo cyoroshye cyane cyo gushyira mu bikorwa.
Ubuyobozi ni ihinduka mu mahame y'akazi cyangwa imikorere isaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi (PPE) byafashwe nk'ibidashobora gukora neza kurusha ibyuma by'ubwubatsi n'ibiro by'ubuyobozi ariko bishobora gufasha mu gukumira ibyagaragaye.
Ubwoko bwose bwa PPE bugomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku kaga ku bakozi, bushyirwe neza hakurikijwe ibisabwa (cth respirator), bukoreshwa neza buri gihe, bugenzurwa buri gihe, bukitabwaho kandi bugasimbuzwa, niba ari ngombwa, kandi bukurwaho neza, bukisukura kandi bugasakwa cyangwa bugatwarwa mu buryo bukwiye kugira ngo birinde kwanduzwa.
Dukurikije ibivugwa n'ikigo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA), akazi gafite ibyago byo kwandura cyane karimo abantu badafite aho bahurira n'abandi bantu ndetse n'abandi bakozi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zisabwa ku kazi kose zirimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi neza, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, amahame yo guhumeka arimo gufunga igihe cyo gukorora no kwitsamura, gutegura amasahani n'ibikoresho by'ibikoresho by'ibikoresho, gutegura gukora ku kazi cyangwa guhinduranya akazi mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, kudashishikariza abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho cyangwa ibikoresho by'abandi, no gukomeza isuku no gusukura mu kazi.
Kumenya no gushyira mu kato abantu bashobora kwandura vuba ni ingamba zikomeye mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi bantu bari ku kazi.
Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyasabye abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero gukomereza mu rugo kugeza igihe bazaba batagifite umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso nibura amasaha 24 badafashe imiti igabanya umuriro cyangwa indi miti ihindura ibimenyetso, kandi bagatanga politiki y'ikiruhuko cyo kurwara, yemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kwita ku bagize umuryango barwaye, kandi abakozi bamenye aya mategeko.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, akazi gafite ibyago byo guhura n'ubwandu bworoheje gakubiyemo akazi gasaba ko umuntu ahura kenshi cyangwa cyane mu birometero bitandatu (1.8 m) n'umuntu utazwi cyangwa ukekwaho ubwandu bwa COVID-19, ariko ashobora kuba yaranduye SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n'ubwandu bw'umuryango bukomeje kuba hafi y'aho ikorerwamo ubucuruzi, cyangwa bitewe n'uko uwo muntu aherutse gukora ingendo mpuzamahanga mu gace karimo ubwandu bwa COVID-19.
Ibi birimo abakozi bafite aho bahurira na rubanda nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo abantu benshi ndetse no mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya ruganda rugaragara. Ingamba z'ubwubatsi kuri aba bantu ndetse n'abandi bafite ibyago byo kwandura zirimo kwinjiza ibyuya by'umwuka bikora cyane, kongera igipimo cy'umuyaga, gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nka za plastiki z'ubwirinzi bwo kwitsamura no gushyiraho amadirishya y'ubuyobozi bw'abakiriya. Ingamba z'ubuyobozi kuri aba bantu ndetse n'abafite ibyago byinshi zirimo gushishikariza abakozi barwaye kuguma mu rugo, gusimbuza amateraniro y'amaso n'itumanaho ry'igihe cyose, gushyiraho gahunda z'amahugurwa, guhagarika ingendo zidakenewe ku bibanza by'icyorezo cya COVID-19 kirimo, guteza imbere gahunda z'ubutabazi bw'ibihe bidasanzwe harimo n'ibiganiro byo gusubiza abakozi, guha abakozi inyigisho n'imyitozo ku bijyanye n'ibyago bya COVID-19 n'indi myitwarire irinda, gutoza abakozi gukoresha imyambaro n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi, gutanga ibikoresho by'ibanze n'ibanze, no gushishoramariza, gushyiraho amabwiriza ku bantu bafite ibyago by'ibanga, kwirinda COVID-19 n'ibyago by'ubwoko buke, gushyiraho ibikoresho by'amaboko ku kazi, cyangwa ku ntoki.
Abakozi bari muri iri tsinda ry'abafite ibyago bakenera gukoresha imashini zifasha guhumeka gake cyane.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, ingamba zikwiye zo kurinda abakozi n'abandi bantu bari mu ndege zirimo gusiga uwo muntu urwaye kure y'abandi bantu mu ntera ya metero 6, guha abakozi kwita kuri uwo muntu, no guha umuntu urwaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa kumusaba gupfuka umunwa n'umwobo we n'umwenda iyo anutse cyangwa anuka.
Abakozi bo mu modoka bagomba kwambara utuntu tw'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi tw'igiceri iyo bita ku muntu urwaye cyangwa iyo bakoreye ku mazi yo mu mubiri cyangwa ahantu hashobora kwandura, kandi hashobora kuba hari ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi by'umubiri mu gihe uwo muntu urwaye afite umuriro, ubwonko buhoraho cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Amasahani n'ibindi bikoresho byo kujugunya bigomba kujugunywa mu mifuka y'ibinyabuzima, kandi ibibanza byanduye bigomba guhumanurwa no gukorwamo imyanda nyuma yaho. Ku byangombwa by'ubucuruzi birimo ubwato bw'ubwato n'ubundi bwato bw'abagenzi, kugenzura akaga birimo guhagarika urugendo mugihe urwaye, kwigunga no kumenyesha ikigo nderabuzima cyo mu bwato ako kanya niba umuntu afite umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso mugihe ari mu bwato.
Ni byiza ko imiti ikurikiranwa ikorerwa mu mazu y'abantu bari mu kato. Ku mashuri n'ibigo byita ku bana, CDC isaba ko hashyirwaho igihe gito cyo gusukura cyangwa gusukura iyo umuntu wafashwe n'iyo ndwara yaba yarigeze kuba mu kigo cy'ishuri, hatitawe ku kuba yakwirakwira mu baturage.
Iyo hari ubwandu buke cyangwa buciriritse mu baturage, ingamba zo kwirinda abantu bashobora gushyira mu bikorwa nko guhagarika ingendo zo mu mirima, amateraniro n'andi materaniro manini nk'amashuri y'imyitozo ngororamubiri n'amashuri y'abaririmbyi cyangwa gusangira mu kabari, kongera umwanya hagati y'ameza, ibihe byo kugera no gutaha byatondetswe, kugabanya abasura batabikwiriye, no gukoresha ahantu hatandukanye ho kwita ku buzima ku bana bafite ibimenyetso nk'iby'ibicurane.
Iyo hari ubwandu bwinshi mu baturage, uretse ingamba zo kwirinda, kongera igihe cyo guhagarika ishuri bishobora gutekerezwa. CDC ibona ko ibyago byo kurwara ku bayobozi bakora ibikorwa bisanzwe ari bike.
