Iyo abantu bagiranye imibonano mpuzabitsina mu gihe cyo gufatwa, abakozi bagomba gusukura no gukata imyenda yabo n'ibikoresho byabo by'akazi mbere yo kubikoresha bakoresheje isuzuma cyangwa imashini yo gusukura inzu, kandi bakagendera ku mabwiriza asanzwe y'imikorere yo gufunga no kwirukana ibikoresho bya bwite by'abantu bikoreshwa no gupakira no kumesa imyenda.
