Hari ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyo abakozi bakora ibikorwa byo gukora aerosol ku, cyangwa mu gukusanya cyangwa mu gutunganya ibipimo by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho.
