Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye ko abarwayi bajya mu kato mu byumba by'indembe bitandukanye bitewe n'uko bakekwaho COVID-19. Usibye PPE, OSHA yasabye ko abarwayi bakora mu ntera ya metero 6 uvuye ku barwayi bazwi, cyangwa bakekwaho kwandura SARS-CoV-2, n'abakora imikorere yo gukora aerosol.
Muri Amerika, ibikoresho byo guhumeka mu maso byemewe na NIOSH N95 cyangwa byiza bigomba gukoreshwa mu rwego rw'ingamba zo kwirinda guhumeka mu buryo bwuzuye kandi bwanditse harimo ibizamini by'ubuziranenge, imyitozo n'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi.
Ubundi bwoko bw'ibinyabuzima bishobora gutanga uburinzi burenze kandi bigatuma abakozi barushaho kumva bamerewe neza.
OMS isaba ko abakozi bo ku biro by'ubuvuzi bajya bambara udupfukamunwa gusa.
Ku bantu bakusanya ibipimo by'ubuhumekero by'abarwayi ba COVID-19, bagakira cyangwa bagatwara abarwayi batakoze aerosol, OMS isaba ko bakoresha udupfukamunwa, udukingirizo tw'amaso, cyangwa udukingirizo tw'amaso, imyenda yo kurinda no kwambara inkweto.
Iyo habaye uburyo bwo gukora aerosol, agapfukamunwa gashyirwa mu cyuma cyo guhumeka cya N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko ibikoresho bya PPE ku isi bitagera ku rwego rwo hejuru, OMS isaba ko hakorwa ibishoboka byose kugira ngo hakoreshwe ibikoresho bya PPE mu buryo bwa telemedicine, mu buryo bw'ibikoresho byabugenewe nko mu madirishya, byemerera gusa abita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 kwinjira mu cyumba, gukoresha ibikoresho bya PPE gusa bikenewe mu kazi runaka, gukomeza gukoresha ibikoresho bya respirateur kimwe ariko ntibikurwe mu gihe urimo kwita ku barwayi benshi bafite icyorezo kimwe, kugenzura no guhuza ibicuruzwa bya PPE, no kudashishikariza abantu gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
