Komeza gushyikirana ku bibazo bijyanye na COVID-19
Tuzohereza umuntu ibaruwa yo gutumira kuri kalendari yawe ku wa kane utaha, saa 14:00 UTC/07:00 PT, kugira ngo haterwe inama yihariye y'abakozi.
Tuzakoresha icyo gihe kugira ngo dusangize abandi amakuru mashya, dusubize ibibazo byawe, kandi dufate akanya ko gushyikirana.
Turi muri ibyo byose kandi turi hano kugira ngo dufashe uko dushoboye kose.
Hagati aho, ushobora gukomeza gushakisha amakuru kuri iyi e-mail, n'andi makuru yose y'ingenzi ajyanye na COVID-19 kuri Office Wiki.
CRT izakomeza kureba ko izi mbuga zose zihora zishyushye kandi ko amakuru yose ari ahantu hamwe.
Turimo kandi gukora ibishoboka byose kugira ngo dukomeze gushyikirana n'abakozi bacu bari mu bihugu byazahajwe cyane n'iki gihe.
Niba ufite ibibazo bijyanye n'ingendo, ibirori, inzira y'akazi cyangwa imbogamizi zo gutanga amakuru, cyangwa se ubufasha ubwo aribwo bwose ukeneye, ntuzatinye kubimenyesha CRT.
Turi hano kugira ngo dufashe mu gutanga ubufasha kandi dufashe mu gihe bibaye ngombwa.
Niba ufite ikintu cy'ibanga cyangwa cy'impungenge, andikira Bryan Judan - Umuyobozi w'ibikorwa by'isi yose muri HR.
Nta na kimwe muri ibyo bintu byahindutse kigomba gufatwa nk'aho ari ukwirengagiza inshingano zacu.
Ariko kandi, ibi byose ni ukwemera ko muri iki gihe, akazi n'inshingano dufite bishobora gukenera guhuzwa mu buryo butandukanye n'uko byahoze mu bihe bya kera.
Ibi ni ingamba twizera ko ari ngombwa kugira ngo dushyigikirane kugirango dukomeze gukora, guha uru rugendo rwacu inkunga zikenewe, n'umurimo isi ishobora kwitega.
Umurimo wacu w'ubugenzuzi uzaba uhari igihe nikigera.
Iki ni igihe cyo gufashanya no kurema umwanya w'imirimo ikomeye izaza mu byumweru biri imbere ndetse wenda no mu mezi ari imbere.
