Angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni enzyme ihuza ku gice cyo hanze (membrane y'ingirabuzimafatizo) y'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu bihimba by'irondoka no mu maraso.
ACE2 ihangana n'ibikorwa bya angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) bifitanye isano no kugabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II no kuzamura Ang (((1-7) bituma iba umuti ushobora kwiringirwa mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora kandi nk'ikigo cyo kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za coronavirus zimwe.
Imiterere y'umuntu ya enzyme ikunze kwitwa hACE2.
Ingirabuzimafatizo ihindura angiotensin 2 ni zinc irimo metaloenzymes iboneka ku butaka bwa endothelium n'izindi ngirabuzimafatizo.
Poroteyine ACE2 ikubiyemo M2 domain ya peptidase ya N-terminal na C-terminal ya cyene ya amino acide transporter ya colectin.
ACE2 ni poroteyine yo mu bwoko bwa 1 y'umwimerere, ifite urubuga rwa enzymes rw'umwimerere rwigaragaza ku bice by'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha no mu bindi binyabuzima.
Urubuga rwo hanze ya ACE2 rwimurirwa ku rubuga rw'urubaho rw'imiterere y'umubiri na indi enteroyine yitwa sheddase, maze umusaruro wa poroteyine ushyirwa mu maraso, amaherezo ukayoherezwa mu cyondo.
ACE2 iboneka mu binyabuzima byinshi: ACE2 ihurira mu ngira z'ingirabuzimafatizo za alveolus ya kabiri ya pumu, entrosite y'uruti rw'umugongo, artery na endothelium ya vein na artery ya musculoskeletal mu binyabuzima byinshi.
Ibimenyetso bya mRNA ACE2 nabyo bigaragara mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko n'icy'ubwonko.
Umurimo w'ibanze wa ACE2 ni ugukora nk'umuhuza wa ACE.
ACE ifata ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin I mu guhuza ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin II.
ACE2 ihindura phenylalanine amino acid ya carboxyl-terminal ya angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kandi ikayishyira mu cyayi cya angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora kandi kwifatanya n'izindi peptide zirimo [des-Arg9]-bradikinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi igenzura uburyo uruhu rw'ibinyabutabire by'indwara ya SLC6A19 by'indwara ya Hartnup rutangazwa.
Nk'umwirondoro w'imikorere, ACE2 ikora nk'ikigo cy'ingenzi cyo kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi zimwe na zimwe zirimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhuza poroteyine ya S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 ku gice cya ACE2 cyo hejuru y'ingirabuzimafatizo bituma virusi na enzyme byinjira mu gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo kiri hagati y'ingirabuzimafatizo.
Gushyiraho kandi bisaba ko poroteyine ya S isuzumwa na TMPRSS2 serine yo mu mubiri, ikoreshwa mu gihe cy'ubushakashatsi nk'umuti ushobora kuvura.
Icyakora, imiryango itandukanye y'abahanga n'inzego zishinzwe kugenzura, byasabye ko hakomeza kubaho uburyo bwo kuvura ACE n'ubuvuzi bwa ARB.
Isuzuma ry'uburyo n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe byasohotse ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012 byabonye ko "imikoreshereze y'imiti ya ACE yari ifitanye isano n'igabanuka rikomeye rya 34% ry'ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'ibicurane ugereranyije n'abayirwanyaga".
Byongeye kandi, "ibyago byo kurwara pneumonia byagabanutse no ku barwayi bavurwa n'abafasha ACE bafite ibyago byo kurwara pneumonia, cyane cyane abafite indwara z'ibinyamaswa n'iza umutima.
Gukoresha ACE-inhibitors byagiye bifatanya no kugabanya umubare w'abapfa bazira pneumonia, nubwo imyanzuro yabo idahuza neza n'ibyago byose byo kwandura pneumonia".
Gusubiramo ACE2 (rhACE2) mu bantu bifatwa nk'umuti w'ubushakashatsi ku byorezo by'ubuhumekero, kandi bigaragara ko byazamura imikorere y'amaraso n'umwuka wa ogisijeni mu ngurube zifite uburwayi bwo guhumeka bw'ibicurane by'ibinyamushongo.
Ubuzima bw'igice cya kabiri cy'umwimerere cya rhACE2 mu bantu ni amasaha 10 kandi intangiriro y'igikorwa ni iminota 30 hiyongereyeho igihe cy'igikorwa (ibihe) cy'amasaha 24.
Bimwe mu byataburuwe byerekana ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti witezweho ku bantu batagaragaza ubwigenge mu byorezo bya angiotensin ya classical renin (RAS inhibitors) cyangwa mu ndwara zigera kuri angiotensin II yagabanyijwe. rhACE2 ya infusion yagenzuwe mu bipimo by'ubuvuzi ku kuvura indwara z'ubuhumekero z'indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Porogaramu ya b'COVID-19 ni porogaramu igendanwa igenewe gufasha gukurikirana abantu mu gisubizo cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-20, ni ukuvuga igikorwa cyo kumenya abantu ("abahuye") bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu wanduye.
Porogaramu nyinshi zikorwa cyangwa zitanzwe n'abategetsi ba leta bashyigikiye mu ntara zitandukanye no mu nzego z'ubutegetsi.
Hari uburyo bwo kubaka porogaramu yo gukurikirana imishyikirano yatangijwe.
Impungenge z'ibanga zongeye kuvuka, cyane cyane ku bijyanye na sisitemu ishingiye ku guhitamo aho porogaramu z'abakoresha ziri.
Ibindi byoroshye harimo gukoresha Bluetooth kugira ngo umuntu ashobore kwandika amakuru y'aho ari kuri telefoni.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byombi byatangaje ko bigiye guhuza imikorere yo gushyigikira porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu y'imikorere ya Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa, ifatanyije na Alipay, yatangije porogaramu yemerera abaturage kureba niba barahuye n'umuntu wanduye COVID-19.
Iri gukoreshwa mu mijyi 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapore, hari porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether iri gukoreshwa.
Porogaramu yakozwe n'umuryango wa IT wo mu karere, yatangijwe nk'isoko ryugurutse kandi izahabwa leta. Macedonia y'Amajyaruguru yatangije "StopKorona!", porogaramu ishingiye kuri Bluetooth igamije gukurikirana abantu bashobora kwandura no gutanga ibisubizo byihuse ku nzego z'ubuzima.
Porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itangazamakuru n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yavuze ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana imishyikirano iri mu cyiciro cy'iterambere ry'inyongera, kandi ko izaba iboneka mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'iyi irateganyijwe muri Ireland no mu Bufaransa ("StopCovid").
Australia na New Zealand zirimo gusuzuma porogaramu zishingiye kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether ya Singapore na BlueTrace. Uburusiya bufite intego yo gushyiraho porogaramu ya geobasicir ku barwayi basanganywe COVID-19 baba i Moscow, igamije gutuma badohoka mu ngo zabo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu muri kaminuza ya Cambridge wigisha iby'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano, yavuze ibibazo byinshi by'ingirakamaro bishobora kuvuka mu mikorere y'ibikoresho, harimo amakosa y'ibanze n'ubushobozi bwo kutagira icyo bikora mu gihe ikoreshwa ry'ibikoresho rifite abantu bake.
Mu guhangana n'impungenge z'uko hashobora kuba hari abantu benshi bakwirakwiza "coronavirus" cyangwa se izindi porogaramu mbi, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku bwoko bw'imiryango ishobora kongeramo porogaramu zijyanye na coronavirus ku bubiko bwayo bwa Apps, ikabishyira ku "b'ibanze" gusa cyangwa ku miryango izwi.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho ingamba nk'izo.
Abashyigikiye ubwiru bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka zo kugenzura abantu benshi bakoresheje porogaramu za coronavirus, by'umwihariko niba ibikorwa remezo by'ubugenzuzi byashyizweho mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus bizakurwaho vuba vuba uko iterabwoba rizaba riheze.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe asaga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko hakorwa ingamba zo kugabanya ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura.
Umuryango utangaza ko hari ibintu umunani byasabwaga mu mishinga ya leta:
igenzura rigomba kuba "ryemewe n'amategeko, ari ngombwa kandi rifite ishingiro";
gukomeza gukurikirana no kugenzura bigomba kuba bifite ingingo zibyanditseho;
