Muri Mata, abahanga mu bya siyansi ba CEPI batangaje ko hari imbuga 10 zitandukanye zikoranabuhanga ziri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi no guteza imbere mu ntangiriro za 2020 mu rwego rwo gukora urukingo rukora neza rwo kurwanya COVID-19.
Urubuga rukuru rugamije gutera imbere mu bushakashatsi bw'umutekano w'icyiciro cya mbere rurimo:
aside ya nucleic (DNA na RNA) (Ukoze Phase 1 n'urukingo rw'icyiciro cya mbere: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
virusi (Umuhanga mu by'ingamba za Phase I n'umukandida: CanSino Biologics, adenovirus type 5).
